hadiths[242]{hadithnumber,text}:
149,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''Jibreel (Aleh.) ney Khana-Kaaba key paas meri do baar imaamat ki. pehli baar unhon-ney Zohar us waqt padhi (jab suraj dhal gaya aur) saya jootey key tasme key barabar ho gaya. phir Asr us waqt padhi jab har chiz ka saya uskey eik jaisa ho gaya. phir maghrib us waqt padhi jab suraj doob gaya aur rozey daar ney iftaar kar liya. phir Isha us waqt padhi jab shafaq padhi. ghaaieb ho gaee. phir Namaze-Fajr us waqt padhi jab Fajr roshan ho gaee aur roze-daar par khana peena haram ho gaya. dusri baar Zohar kal ki Asr key waqt padhi jab har chiz ka saya uskey jaisa ho gaya. phir Asr us waqt padhi jab har chiz ka saya uskey do jaisa ho gaya. phir maghrib uskey awwal waqt hi mein padhi (jaisey pehli baar mein padhi thi) phir Isha us waqt padhi jab eik tihai raat guzar gaee. phir Fajr us waqt padhi jab ujala ho gaya. phir Jibreel ney meri taraf mutawajjeh ho kar kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! yehi aap sey pehley key anbiya ke namaz ke waqt they. aap ki namazon ke oqaat (waqt) bhi unhi dono waqton ke darmiyan hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Abu-Hurera , Barida , abu-Musa , abu-Masood Ansari , abu-Saeed , Jabir , Amr bin Haram , Bara aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
150,Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''Jibreel ney meri imaamat ki.''  phir unhon-ney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees ki tarah usi mafhoom ki hadees zikr ki. albatta unhon-ney is mein Asr ki namaz wala tukda zikr nahin kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.  aur ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : namaz ke waqt ke silsiley mein sab sey sahih Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) wali hadees hai jisey unhon-ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey marfooan riwayat kiya hai.
151,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''namaz ka eik awwal waqt hai aur eik aakhiri waqt, Zohar ka awwal waqt wo hai jab suraj dhal jaey aur uska aakhiri waqt wo hai jab Asr ka waqt shuru ho jaey, aur Asr ka awwal waqt wo hai jab Asr ka waqt (eik jaise sey) shuru ho jaey aur aakhiri waqt wo hai jab suraj peela ho jaey, aur maghrib ka awwal waqt wo hai jab suraj doob jaey aur aakhiri waqt wo hai jab shafaq padhi. ghaaieb ho jaey, aur Isha ka awwal waqt wo hai jab shafaq ghaaieb ho jaey aur uska aakhir waqt wo hai jab aadhi raat ho jaey, aur Fajr ka awwal waqt wo hai jab Fajr (saadiq) tulu ho jaey aur aakhiri waqt wo hai jab suraj nikal jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat aai hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke oqaat (waqt) ke silsile mein Aamash ki Mujahid sey riwayat Muhammad bin Fuzel ki Aamash sey riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai, Muhammad bin Fuzel ki hadees ghalat hai is-mein Muhammad bin Fuzel sey chook hui hai, is riwayat ko Abu-Is'haq Fazaari ney Aamash sey aur Aamash ney Mujahid sey riwayat kiya hai, Mujahid kehtey hain ke kaha jata tha ke namaz ka eik awwal waqt hai aur eik aakhir waqt hai, phir Muhammad bin Fuzel wali sabiqa hadees ki tarah usi ke hum maana ki hadees bayan ki."
152,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas eik shakhs aaya, usney aap sey namaz ke waqt ke barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : tum hamarey sath qiyam karo (tumhen namaz ke waqt malum ho jaeyngey) Insha Allah, phir aap-ney Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney iqaamat kahi jab Fajr (saadiq) tulu ho gaee phir aap ney hukm diya to unhoney suraj dhalney ke baad iqaamat kahi to aap ney Zohar padhi, phir aap ney unhen hukm diya to unhoney iqaamat kahi aap ney Asr padhi us waqt suraj roshan aur buland tha, phir jab suraj doob gaya to aap ney unhen maghrib ka hukm diya, phir jab shafaq ghaaieb ho gaee to aap ney unhen Isha ka hukm diya to unhoney iqaamat kahi, phir doosrey din unhen hukm diya to unhoney Fajr ko khub ujala kar ke padha, phir aap ney unhen Zohar ka hukm diya to unhoney thanda kiya, aur khub thanda kiya, phir aap ney unhen Asr ka hukm diya aur unhon-ney iqaamat kahi to us waqt suraj uskey aakhir waqt mein us sey ziyada tha jitna pehley din tha (yani doosrey din Asr mein takheer (deri) hui), phir aap ney unhen maghrib mein der karney ka hukm diya to unhoney maghrib ko shafaq key doobney sey kuchh pehley tak muakhkhar (der) kiya, phir aap ney unhen Isha ka hukm diya to unhoney jab tihai raat khatam ho gaee to iqaamat kahi, phir aap ney farmaya : ''namaz key oqaat (waqt) key barey mein poochhney wala kahan hai? ''to us aadmi ney arz kiya : main hun, aap ney farmaya : ''namaz key oqaat (waqt) inhin dono ke beech mein hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
153,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Fajr padha letey to phir aurten chaadaron mein lipti hui laut'tin wo andherey ki wajeh sey pehchani nahin jati thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Anas , aur Qaila binte Makhrima (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur isi ko Sahaba kiram jin-mein Abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma bhi shamil hain aur unke baad ke Tabe-een mein sey bahut sey ehle-ilm ney pasand kiya hai, aur yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain ke Fajr (andherey) mein padhna mustahab hai."
154,"mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ''Fajr khub ujala kar ke padho, kyonkey is mein ziyada sawab hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Raafey bin khadij ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Barza Aslami, Jabir aur Bilal (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey kaee ehle-ilm ki raey namaze Fajr ujala honey par padhney ki hai. yehi Sufiyan Sory bhi kehtey hain. aur Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke  ''ujala hone'' ka matlab ye hai ke Fajr wazeh ho jaey aur iskey tulu mein koi shak na rahey  ka ye matlab nahin ke namaz takheer (der) sey ada ki jaey."
155,"Zohar ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey badh kar jaldi karney wala mainey kisi ko nahin dekha, aur na abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma sey badh kar jaldi karney wala kisi ko dekha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Jabir bin Abdullah , Khubab , abu-Barza , ibne-Masood , Zaid bin Sabit , Anas aur Jabir bin Samra (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain aur Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- aur isi ko Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein ehle-ilm ney ikhtiyar kiya hai."
156,Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaze Zohar us waqt padhi jis waqt soorj dhal gaya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai aur ye is baab mein sab sey achi hadees hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadees aai hai.
157,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''jab garmi sakht ho to namaz thanda honey par padho padhi. kyonkey garmi ki tezi jahannam ki bhaap sey hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Saeed , Abu-Zar , ibne-Umar , Mughira , aur Qasim bin Safwan key baap abu-Musa , ibne-Abbas aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- is silsiley mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi riwayat hai jisey unhon-ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey riwayat ki hai, lekin ye sahih nahin. 4- ehle-ilm mein kuchh logon ne sakht garmi mein Zohar takheer sey padhney ko pasand kiya hai. yehi ibne-Mubarak , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. Shafai kehtey hain : Zohar thanda kar ke padhney ki baat us waqt ki hai jab masjid waley door sey aatey hon , raha akeley namaz padhney wala aur wo shakhs jo apney hi logon ki masjid mein namaz padhta ho to main uskey liye yehi pasand karta hun ke wo sakht garmi mein bhi namaz ko der sey na padhey. 5- jo log garmi ki shiddat mein Zohar ko der sey padhney ki taraf gaey hain unka mazhab ziyada behtar aur ittiba key ziyada laaiq hai, rahi wo baat jiski taraf Shafai ka rujhan hai ke ye rukhsat (chhot) uskey liye hai jo door sey aata hota ke logon ko pareshani na ho to Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees mein kuchh aisi baaten hain jo us chiz par dalalat karti hain jo Imam Shafai key qol key khilaf hain. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : hum log eik safar mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key sath they, Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney namaz Zohar key liye Azan di, to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''Bilaal ! thanda ho janey do , thanda ho janey do'' (ye hadees aagey aa rahi hai), ab agar baat aisi hoti jiski taraf Shafai gaey hain, to us waqt thanda karney ka koi matlab na hota, isliye ke safar mein sab log ikhatta they, unhen door sey aaney ki zarurat na thi."
158,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eik safar mein they, sath mein Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney iqaamat kehney ka irada kiya to aap ney farmaya : ''thanda ho janey do.'' unhon-ney phir iqaamat kehney ka irada kiya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya : ''zohar ko thanda kar key padh.'' wo kehtey hain (zohar takheer sey padhi qaee) yahan tak ke humne teelon ka saya dekh liya tab unhon-ne iqaamat kahi phir aap ne namaz padhi, phir farmaya : ''garmi ki tezi jahannam ki bhaap sey hai. lihaza namaz thandey mein padha karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
159,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr padhi us haal mein ke dhoop un ke kamrey mein thi, un ke kamrey ke andar ka saya purab wali deewar par nahin chadha tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas , Abu Arwaa , Jabir aur Raafey bin khadij (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain,  aur Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey Asr ko muakhkhar karney ki bhi riwayat ki jati hai jisey unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey riwayat kiya hai. lekin ye sahih nahin hai. 3- Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney jin mein umr , Abdullah bin Masood , Aaisha aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) bhi shamil hain aur Tabe-een mein sey kaee logon ney isi ko ikhtiyar kiya hai ke Asr jaldi padhi jaey aur is mein takheer karney ko un logon ney makrooh samjha hai isi ke qaayal Abdullah bin Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi hain."
160,"wo Basra mein jis waqt Zohar padh kar lotey to wo Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key paas unke ghar aaye, unka ghar masjid ke baghal hi mein tha. Anas bin Malik ne kaha : utho chalo Asr padho, to humne uth kar namaz padhi, jab padh chukey to unho-ne kaha ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : ''ye munafiq ki namaz hai ke betha suraj ko dekhta rahey, yahan tak ke jab wo shetan ki dono seengon ke darmiyan aa jaey to uthey aur chaar thongein maar ley, aur un mein Allah ko thoda hi yad karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
161,Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar main tum logon sey ziyada jaldi kartey they aur tum log Asr mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey ziyada jaldi kartey ho.
162,ye hadees Ismail bin Aleh se ba-tareeq (ibne-Jurej an ibne-Abi Muleka an Umme-Salma) isi tarah riwayat ki gaee hai. aur mujhey apni kitab mein iski sanad yun mili ke mujhey Ali bin Hajar ney khabar di unhon-ne Ismail bin Ibrahim se aur Ismail ne ibne Juraij se riwayat ki hai.
163,Ibne Juraij se riwayat ziyada sahih hai.
164,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maghrib us waqt padhtey jab suraj doob jata aur pardey mein chup jata. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Salma bin Al Aqwaa wali hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir , Sunabihi , Zaid bin Khalid , Anas , Raafey bin khadij , abu-Ayyub , Umme-Habiba , Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees unse moqufan riwayat ki gaee hai aur yehi ziyada sahih hai. 4- aur Sunabihi ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nahin suna hai, wo to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key daur ke hain. 5- aur yehi qol Sahaba kiram aur unke baad Tabe-een mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka hai. un logon ne namaze maghrib jaldi padhney ko pasand kiya hai aur usey muakhkhar karney ko makrooh samjha hai, yahan tak ke baaz logon ka kehna hai ke maghrib ka eik hi waqt hai padhi. , ye tamam hazraat Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki is hadees ki taraf gaey hain jis mein hai ke Jibreel ney aap ko namaz padhaai aur yehi ibne-Mubarak aur Shafai ka qol hai."
165,is namaz Isha key waqt ko logon mein sab sey ziyada main janta hun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey teesri taareekh ka chaand doobney key waqt padhtey they.
166,isi sanad sey isi tarah riwayet hui hai. Imam Tirmizi ne pehley Abu Awaana ka tariqa zikr kiya phir Hushaim ke tareeqe ka aur farmaya : Abu Awaana wali hadees hamarey nazdik ziyada sahih hai.
167,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''agar main apni ummat par dushwaar na samajhta to main Isha ko tihai raat ya aadhi raat tak der kar ke padhney ka hukm deta.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir bin Samura , Jabir bin Abdullah , abu-Barza , ibne-Abbas , abu Saeed Khudri , Zaid bin Khalid aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) se bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur isi ko Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een waghaira mein se aksar ehle-ilm ne pasand kiya hai. un ki raey hai ke Isha takheer (der) sey padhi jaey, aur yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain."
168,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Isha sey pehley soney aur uskey baad baat cheet karney ko napasand farmatey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Barza ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Abdullah bin Masood aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- aur aksar ehle-ilm ne namaze Isha sey pehley soney aur uskey baad baat karney ko makrooh kaha hai, aur baaz ne iski ijazat di hai, Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain : aksar hadisein karaahat par dalalat karney wali hain, aur baaz logon ne Ramzan mein Isha sey pehley soney ki ijazat di hai."
169,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) musalmanon ke baaz maamlat mein sey abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key sath raat mein guftgu kartey aur main un dono ke sath hota tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr , Aus bin Huzefa aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een aur unke baad key logon mein sey ehle-ilm ney Isha ke baad baat karney ke silsiley mein ikhtilaf kiya hai. kuchh logon ne Isha ke baad baat karney ko makrooh jana hai aur kuchh logon ne uski rukhsat (choot) di hai, ba-sharte-ke ye koi ilmi guftgu ho ya koi aisi zarurat ho jiske baghair chaara na ho padhi. aur aksar hadeesen rukhsat ke bayan mein hain, isi ke saath Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hui hai ke aap ne farmaya : ''baat sirf wo kar sakta hai jo namaze Isha ka muntazir ho ya musafir ho.''"
170,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey puchha gaya : kon sa amal sab sey afzal hai? to aap ney farmaya : ''awwal waqt mein namaz padhna.''
171,"Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un-se farmaya : ''Ali ! teen chizon mein der na karo : namaz ko jab uska waqt ho jaey, janaze ko jab aa jaey, aur bewa aurat (ke nikah ko) jab tumhen uska koi kuf (saathi) mil jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
172,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' namaz awwal waqt mein Allah ki raza-mandi ka moojib hai aur aakhiri waqt mein Allah ki maafi ka moojib hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, 3- aur is baab mein Ali , ibne-Umar , Aaisha aur ibne-Masood (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- Umme farwa ki) ooper wali) hadees ( number : 170 ( Abdullah bin umr Umri hi sey riwayat ki jati hai aur ye muhaddeseen key nazdik qawi nahin hain, is hadees mein log un sey riwayat karney mein iztirab ka shikar hain aur wo Sadooq hain, Yahya bin Saeed ney unkey hifz key talluq sey un par kalam kya hai."
173,"eik shakhs ney ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kon sa amal sab sey achcha hai? unhoney bataya ke mainey uskey barey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey puchha to aap ney farmaya : '' namaz ko uskey waqt par padhna ''. mainey arz kya : aur kya hai? Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : '' waliden key sath husne-suluk karna '' , mainey arz kya : ( uskey baad (aur kya hai? Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : '' Allah ki raah mein jihad karna ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
174,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney koi namaz uskey aakhiri waqt mein do baar nahin padhi yahan tak ke Allah ney aap ko wafat dey di . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai aur iski sanad muttasil nahin hai, 2- Shafai kehtey hain : namaz ka awwal waqt afzal hai aur jo cheezen awwal waqt ki afzaliyat par dalalat karti hain minjumla (sabki sab) unhi mein sey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) , abu-Bakar , aur umr Raziallahu anhuma ka usey pasand farmana hai. ye log usi chiz ko mamool banatey they jo afzal ho aur afzal chiz ko nahin chhodtey they. aur ye log namaz ko awwal waqt mein padhtey they."
175,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jis sey Asr faut ho gaee goya uska ghar aur maal lut gaya ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Barida aur naufal bin Muawiya Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
176,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' Abu-Zar ! merey baad kuch aisey umra ( hukkaam ( hongey jo namaz ko maar dalengey padhi. , to tum namaz ko uskey waqt par padh lena padhi. namaz apney waqt par padh li gaee to imaamat wali namaz tumharey liye nafl hogi , warna tum ney apni namaz mehfooz kar hi li hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abdullah bin Masood aur Ubada bin Samit Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, 3- yehi ehle-ilm mein sey kaee logon ka qol hai, ye log mustahab samajhtey hain ke aadmi namaz apney waqt par padh ley jab Imam usey muakhkhar kerey. phir wo Imam key sath bhi padhey aur pehli namaz hi aksar ehle-ilm key nazdik farz hogi۔"
177,"logon ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey namaz sey apney so janey ka zikr kya to aap ney farmaya : '' so janey mein qusur aur kami nahin . qusur aur kami to jaagney mein hai, (ke jaagta rahey aur na padhey ( lihaza tum mein sey koi jab namaz bhool jaey, ya namaz sey so jaey, to jab usey yad aaye padh ley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Qatada ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , abu-Maryam , Imran bin Husain , Juber bin Mut-im , abu-Juhaifa , abu-Saeed , Amr bin Umayya Zamri aur Zu-Mikhmar (jinhen Zu-Mikhbar bhi kaha jata hai, aur ye Najashi key bhatijey hain ( (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- ehle-ilm key darmiyan us shakhs key barey mein ikhtilaf hai ke jo namaz sey so jaey ya usey bhool jaey aur aisey waqt mein jaagey ya usey yad aaye jo namaz ka waqt nahin maslan suraj nikal raha ho ya doob raha ho to baaz log kehtey hain ke usey padh ley jab jaagey ya yad aaye bhale hi suraj nikalney ka ya doobney ka waqt ho, yehi Ahmed , Is-haq bin Raahviya , Shafai aur Malik ka qol hai. aur baaz kehtey hain ke jab tak suraj nikal na jaey ya doob na jaey na padhey . pehla qol hi raajeh hai, kyonkey ye namaz sabab wali) qaza ( hai aur sabab wali mein waqt ki pabandi nahin hai."
178,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs namaz bhool jaey to chaahiye ke jab yad aaye padh ley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Samra aur abu-Qatada Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki jati hai ke unhoney us shakhs key barey mein jo namaz bhool jaey kaha ke wo padh ley jab bhi usey yad aaye chahey waqt ho ya na ho. yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, aur abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai ke wo Asr mein so gaey aur suraj doobney key waqt uthey , to unhoney namaz nahin padhi jab tak ke suraj doob nahin gaya۔ ehle-koofa key kuch log usi taraf gaey hain. rahey hamarey as-haab yani muhaddeseen to wo Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) hi key qol ki taraf gaey hain."
179,"Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mushrekin ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khandaq key din chaar namazon sey rok diya . yahan tak ke raat jitni Allah ney chahi guzar gaee , phir aap ney Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney Azan kahi , phir iqaamat kahi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney Zohar padhi , phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney iqaamat kahi to aap ney Asr padhi , phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney iqaamat kahi to aap ney maghrib padhi , phir unhoney iqaamat kahi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney Isha padhi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein abu-Saeed aur Jabir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ki sanad mein koi burai nahin hai siwaye uskey ke abu-Ubaida ney apney baap Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey nahin suna hai, 3- aur chhoti hui namazon key silsiley mein baaz ehle-ilm ney usi ko pasand kya hai ke aadmi jab un ki qaza karey to har namaz key liye alag alag iqaamat kahey aur agar wo alag alag iqaamat na kahey to bhi wo usey kafi hoga, aur yehi Shafai ka qol hai."
180,"umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney khandaq key roz kuffar Quraish ko bura bhala kehtey huye kaha ke Allah key Rasool ! main Asr nahin padh saka yahan tak ke suraj doobney key qarib ho gaya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' Allah ki qism ! mainey usey ( ab bhi) nahin padhi hai'' , wo kehtey hain : phir hum wadi Bat'haan mein utrey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu kya aur hamney bhi wuzu kya, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney suraj doob janey key baad pehley Asr padhi phir uskey baad maghrib padhi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai padhi. ."
181,Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' « صلاة وسطیٰ » Asr ki salaat hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
182,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' « صلاة وسطیٰ » Asr ki salaat hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- « صلاة وسطیٰ » key silsiley mein Samra ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- is bab mein Ali , Abdullah bin Masood , Zaid bin Sabit , Aaisha , Hafsa , Abu-Hurera aur abu-Hashim bin Aqba (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke Ali bin Abdullah ( ibne-Madeeni (ka kehna hai : Hasan Basri ki hadees jisey unhoney Samra bin Jundub sey riwayat kya hai, sahih hadees hai, jisey unhoney samra sey suna hai, 4- Sahaba kiram aur unkey ilawa deegar logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai, Zaid bin Sabit aur Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ka kehna hai ke « صلاة وسطیٰ » Zohar ki salaat hai, ibne-Abbas aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) kehtey hain ke « صلاة وسطیٰ » subh ki salaat ( yani Fajr ( hai padhi. , 5- wo Habib bin Shahid kehtey hain ke mujh sey Muhammad bin Sirin ney kaha ke tum Hasan Basri sey puchho ke unhoney Aqeeqa ki hadees kis sey suni hai? to mainey un sey puchha to unhoney kaha ke mainey usey Samra bin Jundub sey suna hai, 6- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke Ali ibne-Madeeni ney kaha hai ke Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey Hasan ka samaa, sahih hai aur unhoney usi hadees sey daleel pakdi hai."
183,"mainey Sahaba kiram (Raziallauh anhum) mein sey kaee logon sey) jin mein umr bin Khattab bhi hain aur wo mujhey sab sey ziyada mehbub hain ( suna ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney Fajr key baad jab tak ke suraj nikal na aaye padhi. aur Asr key baad jab tak ke doob na jaey namaz padhi. padhney sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees jisey unhoney umr sey riwayat ki hai, Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , ibne-Masood , Aqba bin Aamir , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Umar , Samra bin Jundub , Abdullah bin Amr , Muaz bin Ifra , Sunabihi ( Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey unhoney nahin suna hai) Salma bin Akwaa , Zaid bin Sabit , Aaisha , Kaab bin Murra , abu-Umama , Amr bin Abasa , Yala ibn Umayya aur Muawiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein sey aksar fuqaha ka yehi qol hai ke unhoney Fajr key baad suraj nikalney tak aur Asr key baad suraj doobney tak namaz padhney ko makrooh jana hai, rahin faut shuda namazein to unhen Asr key baad ya Fajr key baad qaza karney mein koi harj nahin, 4- Shoba kehtey hain ke Qatada ney abul-Aaliya sey sirf teen cheezen suni hain. eik umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees jis mein hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney Asr key baad namaz padhney sey mana farmaya hai jab tak ke suraj na doob jaey, aur Fajr key baad bhi jab tak ke suraj nikal na aaye, aur) dusri ( ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees jisey unhoney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey kisi key liye ye munasib nahin ke wo ye kahey ke main Yunus bin Matti sey behtar hun aur) teesri ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ke qaazi teen qism key hotey hain ''."
184,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney Asr key baad do rakatein padhein , isliye ke aap key paas kuch maal aaya tha, jiski wajeh sey aap ko Zohar key baad ki dono rakatein padhney ka moqey nahin mil saka tha to aap ney unhen Asr key baad padha phir aap ney unhen dobara nahin padha padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Umme-Salma , Memuna aur abu-Musa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- deegar kaee logon ney bhi Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey riwayat ki hai ke aap ney Asr baad do rakatein padhein ye us chiz key khilaf hai jo aap sey riwayat ki gaee hai ke aap ney Asr key baad jab tak suraj doob na jaey namaz padhney sey mana farmaya hai, 4- ibne-Abbas wali hadees jis mein hai ke aap ney dobara aisa nahin kya, sab sey ziyada sahih hai, 5- Zaid bin Sabit sey bhi ibne-Abbas hi ki hadees ki tarah marvi hai, 6- 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi kaee hadisein marvi hain, neez un sey ye bhi riwayat kya gaya hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bhi unkey yahan Asr key baad aatey do rakatein padhtey, 7- neez unhoney Umme-Salma key wastey sey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey riwayat ki hai ke aap Asr key baad jab tak suraj doob na jaey aur Fajr key baad jab tak nikal na aaye namaz padhney sey mana farmatey they. 8- aksar ehle-ilm ka ittifaq bhi isi par hai ke Asr key baad jab tak suraj doob na jaey aur Fajr key baad jab tak nikal na aaye namaz padhna makrooh hai siwaye un namazon key jo is sey mustashna hain maslan Makka mein Asr key baad tawaf ki dono rakatein padhna yahan tak suraj doob jaey aur Fajr key baad yahan tak ke suraj nikal aaye , is silsiley mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey rukhsat marvi hai, Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein sey ehle-ilm mein sey kuch logon ney yehi kaha hai. aur yehi Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain, Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney Asr aur Fajr key baad Makka mein bhi namaz padhney ko makrooh jana hai, Sufiyan Sory, Malik bin Anas aur baaz ehle-koofa isi key qaail hain."
185,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jo nafli namaz padhna chahey uskey liye har do Azan padhi. key darmiyan namaz hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Zuber Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Sahaba kiram key darmiyan maghrib sey pehley ki namaz key silsiley mein ikhtilaf paya jata hai, un mein sey baaz key nazdik maghrib sey pehley namaz nahin, aur Sahaba mein sey kaee logon sey marvi hai ke wo log maghrib sey pehley Azan aur iqaamat key darmiyan do rakatein padhtey they, 4- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke agar koi unhen padhey to behtar hai, aur ye un dono key nazdik mustahab hai."
186,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jisney suraj nikalney sey pehley Fajr ki eik rakat pa li to usney Fajr pa li , aur jisney suraj doobney sey pehley Asr ki eik rakat pa li to usney Asr pa li '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- hamarey as-haab , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain, ye hadees unkey nazdik sahibe-uzr key liye hai maslan aisey shakhs key liye jo namaz sey so gaya aur suraj nikalney ya doobney key waqt bedaar huwa ho ya usey bhool gaya ho aur wo suraj nikalney ya doobney key waqt usey namaz yad aai ho."
187,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney baghair khof aur barish padhi. key Madiney mein Zohar aur Asr ko eik sath aur maghrib aur Isha ko eik sath jama kya padhi. . ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha gaya ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka us sey kya mansha thi ? kaha : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka mansha ye thi ke aap apni ummat ko kisi pareshani mein na dalen . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees kaee sanadon sey marvi hai, ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey uskey khilaf bhi marfooan marvi hai."
188,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney baghair uzr key do namazein eik sath padhein wo kabeera gunahon key darwazon mein sey eik darwazey mein dakhil huwa '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Wehnash hi abu-Ali Rehbi hain aur wohi Husain bin Qais bhi hai. ye muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hai, Ahmed waghera ney uski tazeef ki hai, 2- aur isi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai ke safar ya Arfa key siwa do namazein eik sath na padhi jaeyn, 3- Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney mareez ko do namazein eik sath jama karney ki rukhsat di hai. yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain, 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke barish key sabab bhi do namazein jama ki ja sakti hain. Shafai , Ahmed , aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. albatta Shafai mareez key liye do namazein eik sath jama karney ko durust qarar nahin detey."
189,"jab hamney ( Madina Munawra main eik raat ( subh ki to hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur mainey aap ko apna khuwab bataya padhi. to aap ney farmaya : '' ye eik sacha khuwab hai, tum utho Bilal key sath jaao wo tum sey oonchi aur lambi aawaz waley hain. aur jo tumhen bataya gaya hai, wo un par pesh karo, wo usey zor sey pukar kar kahin '' , jab umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki Azan suni to apna teh band khinchtey huye Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye , aur arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq key sath Nabi bana kar bheja hai, mainey ( bhi) isi tarah dekha hai jo unhoney kaha , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah ka shukr hai, ye baat aur pakki ho gaee ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- aur Ibrahim bin Saad ney ye hadees Muhammad bin Is-haq sey us sey bhi ziyada kamil aur ziyada lambi riwayat ki hai. aur is mein unhoney Azan key kalmaat ko do-do baar aur iqaamat key kalmaat ko eik eik baar kehney ka waqia zikr kya hai, 4- Abdullah bin Zaid hi ibn abde-rabba hain aur unhen ibne-Abde-rabba bhi kaha jata hai, siwaye Azan key silsiley ki us eik hadees key hamen nahin malum ke un ki Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey koi aur bhi hadees sahih hai, albatta Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim Mazni ki kaee hadisein hain jinhen wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain, aur ye Ibaad bin Tameem key chacha hain."
190,"jis waqt musalman Madina aaye to wo ikhattey ho kar oqaat namaz ka andaza lagatey they, koi namaz key liye pukar na lagata tha, eik din un logon ney is silsiley mein guftgu ki padhi. chunanche un mein sey baaz logon ney kaha : Nasara key naaqoos ki tarah koi naaqoos bana lo, baaz ney kaha ke tum yahudiyon key qarn ki tarah koi qarn ( yani kisi janwer ka seeng ( bana lo. ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : is par umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya tum koi aadmi nahin bhej saktey jo namaz key liye pukarey. to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Bilal utho jao namaz key liye pukaro ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki) us ( riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. ( jisey Bukhari o Muslim aur deegar muhaddeseen ney riwayat kya hai) padhi. ."
191,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen bitha kar Azan ka eik-eik lafz sikhaya. Ibrahim bin abdul-Azeez bin abdul-Malik bin abi Mehzura kehtey hain : is tarah jaisey hamari Azan hai. Bishr kehtey hain to mainey un sey yani Ibrahim sey kaha : isey mujh par dohraiye to unhoney tarjee key sath Azan ka zikr kya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Azan key silsiley mein abu Mehzura wali hadees sahih hai, kaee sanadon sey marvi hai, 2- aur usi par Makka mein amal hai aur yehi Shafai ka qol hai."
192,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen Azan key 19 kalmaat padhi. aur iqaamat key satrah kalmaat sikhaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm Azan key silsiley mein usi taraf gaey hain, 3- abu Mehzura sey ye bhi riwayat hai ke wo iqaamat ikehri kehtey they."
193,"Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya gaya tha ke wo Azan dohri aur iqaamat ikahri kahen. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadees aai hai, 2- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai, aur Malik, Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain."
194,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein Azan aur iqaamat dono dohri hoti thin . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Zaid ki hadees ko Wakee ney b-tareeq « Aamash an Amr bin Murra an Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela » riwayat kya hai ke Abdullah bin Zaid ney khuwab mein Azan (ka waqia ( dekha , aur Shoba ney b-tareeq « Amr bin Murra an Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela » ye riwayat ki hai ke Muhammad Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key as-haab ney hum sey bayan kya hai ke Abdullah bin Zaid ney khuwab mein Azan (ka waqia ( dekha , 2- ye ibne-Abi Leila ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai padhi. , Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila ney Abdullah bin Zaid sey nahin suna hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke Azan aur iqaamat dono dohri hain yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak aur ehle-koofa ka qol hai, 4- ibne-Abi Leila sey murad Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila hain. wo koofa key qazi they, unhoney apney walid sey nahin suna hai albatta wo eik shakhs sey riwayat kartey hain aur wo unkey walid sey ."
195,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : '' Bilal ! jab tum Azan do to thehar thehar kar do aur jab iqaamat kaho to jaldi jaldi kaho , aur apni Azan o iqaamat key darmiyan is qadr waqfa rakho ke khaney peeney wala apney khaney peeney sey aur pakhana peshab ki hajat mehsus karney wala apni hajat sey farigh ho jaey aur us waqt tak ( iqaamat kehney key liye ( khadey na ho jab tak ke mujhey na dekh lo."
196,"Abdul-Mun-im sey isi tarah ki hadees marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey yani Abdul-Mun-im hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur ye majhool sanad hai, Abdul-Mun-im Basra key Shekh hain ( yani zaeef Raavi hain ( ."
197,"mainey Bilal ko Azan detey dekha , wo ghoom rahey they padhi. apna chehra idhar aur udhar pher rahey they aur unki ungliyan unkey dono kanon mein thin, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney surkh khemey mein they, wo chamdey ka tha, Bilal aap key samney sey neza ley kar nikley aur usey Bat'haa ( maidan ( mein gaad diya . phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uski taraf munh kar key namaz padhaai . us neze key aagey sey padhi. kuttey aur gadhey guzar rahey they. aap eik surkh chadar pehney huye they, main goya aap ki pindliyon ki safedi dekh raha hun۔ Sufiyan kehtey hain : hamara khayal hai wo chadar yamni thi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Juhaifa ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo us chiz ko mustahab samajhtey hain ke muazzan Azan main apni dono ungliyan apney kanon mein dakhil kerey. 3- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke wo iqaamat mein bhi apni dono ungliyan dono kanon mein dakhil kerega, yehi Auzaai ka qol hai."
198,"mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Fajr key siwa kisi bhi namaz mein taswib padhi. na karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein abu Mehzura (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ko hum sirf abu-Israail Mulaai ki sanad sey jantey hain. aur abu-Israail ney ye hadees Hakam bin utaibaa sey nahin suni, balke unhoney usey Hasan bin Imaara sey aur Hasan ney Hakam bin Uteba sey riwayat kya hai, 3- abu-Israail ka naam Ismail bin abi Is-haq hai, aur wo ehle-hadees key nazdik ziyada qawi nahin hain, 4- ehle-ilm ka taswib ki tafseer key silsiley mein ikhtilaf hai; baaz kehtey hain : taswib Fajr ki Azan mein « Assalaatu Khairum-minan-naum » '' namaz neend sey behtar hai'' kehney ka naam hai ibne-Mubarak aur Ahmed ka yehi qol hai, Is-haq kehtey hain : taswib uskey ilawa hai, taswib makrooh hai, ye aisi chiz hai jisey logon ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baad ejaad ki hai, jab muazzan Azan deta aur log takheer kartey to wo Azan aur iqaamat key darmiyan : «qad qamatis-salah, hayyi alas-salah, hayyi alal-falah» kehta , 5- aur jo Is-haq bin Raahviya ney kaha hai darasal yehi wo taswib hai jisey ehle-ilm ney napasand kya hai aur isi ko logon ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baad ejaad kya hai, ibne-Mubarak aur Ahmed ki jo tafseer hai ke taswib ye hai ke muazzan Fajr ki Azan mein : « Assalaatu Khairum-minan-naum » kahey to ye kehna sahih hai, usey bhi taswib kaha jata hai aur ye wo taswib hai jisey ehle-ilm ney pasand kya aur durust jana hai, Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai ke wo Fajr mein « Assalaatu Khairum-minan-naum » kehtey they, aur Mujahid sey marvi hai ke main Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma key sath eik masjid mein dakhil huwa jis mein Azan di ja chuki thi. hum is mein namaz padhna chah rahey they. itney mein muazzan ney taswib ki, to Abdullah bin umr masjid sey bahar nikley aur kaha : is bid-ati key paas sey hamarey sath nikal chalo, aur us masjid mein unhoney namaz nahin padhi, Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ney is taswib ko jisey logon ney baad mein ejaad kar liya tha napasand kya."
199,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey Fajr ki Azan deney ka hukm diya to mainey Azan di, phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney iqaamat kehni chahi to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' qabila Sadaa key eik shakhs ney Azan di hai aur jisney Azan di hai wohi iqaamat kahega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- Ziyad (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat ko hum sirf Afriqi ki sanad sey jantey hain aur Afriqi muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain. Yahya bin Saeed Qataan waghera ney unki tazeef ki hai. Ahmed kehtey hain : main Afriqi ki hadees nahin likhta, lekin mainey Muhammad bin Ismail ko dekha wo unkey mamley ko qawi qarar dey rahey they aur keh rahey they ke ye maqaribul-hadees hain, 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke jo Azan dey wohi iqaamat kahey."
200,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Azan wohi dey jo baa-wuzu ho '' padhi. .
201,"Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : namaz key liye wohi Azan dey jo baa-wuzoo ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye pehli hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. 2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ko ibne Wahab ne marfoo riwayat nahin kiya, ye Waleed bin Muslim ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. 3- Zohri ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey nahin suna hai. 4- baghair wuzu ke Azan deney mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, baaz ney isey makrooh kaha hai aur yehi Shafai aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai, aur baaz ehle-ilm ney is silsiley mein rukhsat (choot) di hai, aur isi key qaail Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak aur Ahmed hain."
202,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka muazzan der karta aur iqaamat nahin kehta tha yahan tak ke jab wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh leta ke aap nikal chukey hain tab wo iqaamat kehta. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) waali hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur hum Israel ki hadees ko jisey unhoney Simaak sey riwayat ki hai, sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain 3- isi tarah baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha hai ke muazzan ko Azan ka ziyada ikhtiyar hai padhi. aur Imam ko iqaamat ka ziyada ikhtiyar hai."
203,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''Bilaal raat hi mein Azan dey detey hain, lihaza tum khatey peetey raho , jab tak ke ibne Umme Maktoom ki Azan na sun lo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein ibne-Masood , Aaisha , Aneesa , Anas , Abu-Zar aur Samura (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 3- raat hi mein Azan keh deney mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke agar raat baqi ho muazzan tabhi Azan keh dey to kafi hai, usey dohraaney ki zarurat nahin, Malik , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai, baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke jab wo raat mein Azan dedey to usey dohraaey, yehi Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain 4- Hammad bin Salma ne ba-tareeqe (Ayub an Nafey an ibne-Umar) riwayat ki hai ke Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney raat hi mein Azan dey di, to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhen hukm diya ke wo pukar kar keh den ke banda so gaya tha. ye hadees ghair mehfooz hai, sahih wo riwayat hai jisey Ubedullah bin umr waghera ney ba-tareeqe Nafey an ibne-Umar riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''Bilaal raat hi mein Azan dey detey hain, lihaza tum khatey peetey raho , jab tak ke ibne Umme Maktoom Azan na dey den. aur Abdul-Azeez bin Abi Rawaad ney Nafey sey riwayat ki hai ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke muazzan ne raat hi mein Azan dey di to umr ne usey hukm diya ke wo Azan dohraaey, ye bhi sahih nahin kyonkey Nafey aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) key darmiyan taalluq khatm hai, aur shayad Hammad bin Salma , ki murad yehi hadees padhi. ho, sahih Ubedullah bin umr doosrey riwayton ki riwayat hai jisey un logon ney Nafey sey , aur Nafey ney ibne-Umar sey aur Zohri ney Salim sey aur Salim ney ibne-Umar sey riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : Bilal raat hi mein Azan dey detey hain. 5- agar Hammad ki hadees sahih hoti to is hadees ka koi maana na hota. jis mein hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''Bilaal raat hi mein Azan detey hain, aap ney logon ko aaney waley zamaney key barey mein hukm diya hai aur farmaya hai ke Bilal raat hi mein Azan dey detey hain'' aur agar aap tulu Fajr sey pehley Azan dey deney par unhen Azan lautaane ka hukm detey to aap ye na farmatey ke ''Bilaal raat hi mein Azan dey detey hain.''  Ali bin Madeeni kehtey hain : Hammad bin Salma wali hadees jisey unhoney Ayub sey, aur Ayub ney Nafey sey, aur Nafey ne ibne-Umar sey aur umr ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki hai ghair mehfooz hai, Hammad bin Salma se is mein chook hui hai."
204,eik shakhs Asr ki Azan ho chukney key baad masjid sey nikla to Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : raha ye to usney Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nafarmani ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki riwayat Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadees hai. 3- Sahaba kiram aur unke baad ke logon mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke Azan ho janey ke baad baghair kisi uzr ke maslan be wuzu ho ya koi naaguzeer zarurat aa padi ho jis ke baghair chaara na ho koi masjid sey na nikle. 4- Ibrahim Nakhai sey marvi hai ke jab tak muazzan iqaamat shuru nahin karta wo bahar nikal sakta hai. 5- hamarey nazdik ye us shakhs key liye hai jiske paas nikalney ke liye koi uzr mojud ho.
205,"main aur merey chacha-zaad bhai dono Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaye to aap ney hum sey farmaya : jab tum dono safar mein ho to Azan do aur iqaamat kaho. aur imaamat wo karey jo tum dono mein bada ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai, un logon ney safar mein Azan ko pasand kiya hai, aur baaz kehtey hain : iqaamat kafi hai, Azan to uskey liye hai jis ka irada logon ko ikhatta karna ho. lekin pehla qol ziyada sahih hai aur yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain."
206,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jisney saat saal tak sawab ki niyat sey Azan di uskey liye jahannam ki aag sey najat likh di jaeygi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees gharib hai. 2-is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood 'Soban' Muawiya , Anas , Abu-Hurera aur abu-Saeed (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur Jabir bin Yazeed Jo'fii ki logon ney zaeef tehraaya hai, Yahya bin Saeed aur Abdur-Rehman bin Mahdi ney unhen tark kiya hua qarar diya hai. 4- agar Jabir Ju'fii na hotey padhi. to ehle-koofa baghair hadees key hotey, aur agar Hammad na hotey to ehle-koofa baghair fiqeh key hotey."
207,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''Imam zaamin hai padhi. aur Muazzan ameen padhi. hai, aey Allah ! to imaamon ko raahe-raast par rakh padhi. aur Muazzan ki maghfirat farma.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Aaisha , Sehal bin Saad aur Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. muallif (hadees jama karne wale) ney hadees key turq aur pehli sanad ki pairwi karne ke zikr karney aur abu-Saaleh ki Aaisha sey riwayat key baad farmaya : mainey abu-Zara'a ko kehtey suna ke abu-Saaleh ki Abu-Hurera sey marvi hadees abu-Saaleh ki Aaisha sey marvi hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. isi ke saath mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke abu-Saaleh ki Aaisha sey marvi hadees ziyada sahih hai aur Bukhari, Ali bin Madini kehtey hain ke abu-Saaleh ki hadees Abu-Hurera sey marvi hadees sabit nahin hai aur na hi abu-Saaleh ki Aaisha sey marvi hadees sahih hai."
208,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''jab tum Azan suno to wesey hi kaho jaisey Muazzan kehta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) wali hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Raafey , Abu-Hurera , Umme-Habiba , Abdullah bin Amr , Abdullah bin Rabeea'a, Aaisha , Muaz bin Anas aur Muawiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Maamar aur kaee riwayton ney Zohri sey Malik ki hadees key jaisi riwayat ki hai, Abdur-Rehman bin Is-haq ney is hadees ko b-tareeq : (Zohri an Saeed bin Musaiyab an abi Huraira an nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) riwayat kiya hai, Malik wali riwayat sab sey sahih hai."
209,sab sey aakhiri wasiyat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney mujhey ye ki ke ''Muazzan aisa rakhna jo Azan ki ujrat na ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai 2- aur ehle-ilm key nazdik amal isi par hai. unhoney makrooh jana hai ke muazzan Azan par ujrat ley aur mustahab qarar diya hai ke muazzan Azan ajr aur sawab ki niyat sey dey.
210,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Muazzan ki Azan sun kar kaha : (وأنا أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له وأن محمدا عبده ورسوله رضيت بالله ربا وبمحمد رسولا وبالإسلام دينا).'' aur main bhi gawahi deta hun ke koi mabood bar-haq nahin siwaye Allah key , wo akela hai uska koi shareek nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain aur main Allah ke rab honey aur Islam ke Deen honey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Rasool honey par razi hun.'' to uskey (sagheera) gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- isey hum sirf Lais bin Saad ki sanad sey jantey hain jisey wo Hakeem bin Abdullah bin Qais sey riwayat kartey hain."
211,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jisney Azan sun kar «اللهم رب هذه الدعوة التامة والصلاة القائمة آت محمدا الوسيلة والفضيلة وابعثه مقاما محمودا الذي وعدته إلا حلت له الشفاعة يوم القيامة» '' aey Allah ! us kamil dawat padhi. aur qaaim honey wali salaat key rab ! ( hamarey Nabi ( Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( ko wasila padhi. aur fazilat padhi. ata kar , aur unhen maqam Mehmood 4- mein pahuncha jis ka tu ney wada farmaya hai'' kaha to uskey liye qiyamat key roz shafaat halal ho jaeygi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Muhammad bin Munkadir key tareeq sey Hasan gharib hai, hum nahin jantey ke Shuaib bin abi Hamza key ilawa kisi aur ney bhi Muhammad bin Munkadir sey riwayat ki hai."
212,Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' Azan aur iqaamat key darmiyan ki dua radd nahin ki jati ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai.
213,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par Meraj ki raat pachas namazein farz ki gaeen, phir kam ki gaeen yahan tak ke (kam kartey kartey) paanch kar di gaeen. phir pukar kar kaha gaya : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)  ! meri baat atal hai, tumhen in paanch namazon ka sawab pachas key barabar mileyga padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Ubada bin Samit , Talha bin Ubedullah , Abu-Zar , abu-Qatada , Malik bin Saa'saa aur abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
214,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''rozaana paanch waqt ki namaz aur eik Juma sey doosra Juma beech ke gunahon ka kaffara hain, jab tak ke kabeera gunah sarzad na hon.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir , Anas aur Hanzala Usaidi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
215,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''baa-jamaa't namaz tanha namaz par sattaais darjey fazilat rakhti hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood , Ubai-bin Kaab , Muaz bin Jabal , abu-Saeed , Abu-Hurera aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain.  3- Nafey ney ibne-Umar sey marfooan riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''namaz ba-jamaat aadmi ki tanha namaz par sattaais darjey fazilat rakhti hai. 4- aam riwayton ney (Sahaba) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey  ''pachchees darjey'' naqal kiya hai, sirf ibne-Umar ney ''sattaais darjey'' ki riwayat ki hai."
216,Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''aadmi ki ba-jamaat namaz uski tanha namaz sey pachchees guna badh kar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
217,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''main ne irada kiya ke apney kuchh nojawanon ko main lakdi key gatthar ikhatta karney ka hukm dun, phir namaz ka hukm dun to khadi ki jaey, phir main un logon (key gharon) ko aag laga dun jo namaz mein hazir nahin hotey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2-is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood , Abu-Darda , ibne-Abbas , Muaz bin Anas aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba mein sey kaee logon sey marvi hai ke jo Azan suney aur namaz mein na aaye to uski namaz nahin hoti. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha hai ke ye zabardasti ke taur par hai. (lekin) kisi ko baghair uzr ke jamaat chhodney ki ijazat nahin."
218,"ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey us shakhs key barey mein puchha gaya jo din ko roza rakhta ho aur raat ko qiyam karta ho. aur jume mein hazir na hota ho, to unhoney kaha : wo jahannam mein hoga. Mujahid kehtey hain : hadees ka mafhoom ye hai ke wo jamaat aur jume mein unse be-raghbati kartey huey (bina dilchaspi ke), unhen haqeer jantey huye aur un mein susti kartey huye hazir na hota ho."
219,"main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key sath Hijjaatul-Wadaa' mein shareek raha. mainey aap key sath masjide Khaif mein Fajr padhi. jab aap ney namaz puri kar li aur hamari taraf mudey to kya dekhtey hain ke logon key aakhir mein (sab sey peechhey) do aadmi hain jinhon-ne aap key sath namaz nahin padhi. aap ney farmaya : ''unhen merey paas lao.''  wo laye gaey, unkey moondhey dar sey phadak rahey they. aap ney puchha : ''tum dono ney hamarey sath namaz kyon nahin padhi?'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! humne apney dairon mein namaz padh li thi. aap ney farmaya : ''aisa na kiya karo, jab tum apney dairon mein namaz padh lo phir masjid aao jis mein jamaat ho rahi ho to logon ke sath bhi padh lo padhi. ye tumharey liye nafl ho jaeygi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Yazeed bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Mihjan Daili aur Yazeed bin Aamir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm mein sey kaee logon ka yehi qol hai. aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain ke jab aadmi tanha namaz padh chuka ho phir usey jamaat mil jaey to wo jamaat key sath dobara namaz padh ley. aur jab aadmi tanha maghrib padh chuka ho phir jamaat paey to wo unkey sath namaz padhey aur eik rakat aur padh kar usey juft (jodaa) bana dey, aur jo namaz usne tanha padhi hai wohi unke nazdik farz hogi."
220,"eik shakhs (masjid) aaya Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) namaz padh chukey they to aap ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey kon iskey sath tijarat kareyga? padhi. eik shakhs khada hua aur usne uske sath namaz padhi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Umama , abu-Musa aur Hakam bin Umer (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba aur Tabe-een mein sey kaee ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai ke jis masjid mein log jamaat sey namaz padh chukey hon is mein (doosri) jamaat sey namaz padhney mein koi harj nahin, yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain. 4- aur baaz doosrey ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke wo tanha tanha namaz padhen, yehi Sufiyan, ibne-Mubarak , Malik , Shafai ka qol hai, ye log tanha tanha namaz padhney ko pasand kartey hain."
221,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : jo Isha ki jamaat mein hazir rahega to usey aadhi raat key qiyam ka sawab milega aur jo Isha aur Fajr dono namazein jamaat sey ada kerega, usey puri raat key qiyam ka sawab milega . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Usman ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar, Abu-Hurera , Anas , Imaara bin Rubiya, Jundub bin Abdullah bin Sufiyan bijli, abi ibn Kaab, abu-Musa aur Barida (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- ye hadees Abdur-Rehman bin abi Umra key tareeq sey Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey moqufan riwayat ki gaee hai, aur kaee dusri sanadon sey bhi ye Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey marfooan marvi hai."
222,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jisney Fajr padhi wo Allah ki panah mein hai to tum Allah ki panah haath sey janey na do '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : hadees Hasan sahih hai.
223,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' andherey mein chal kar masjid aaney walon ko qiyamat key din kamil Noor ( bharpur ujaley ( ki basharat dey do ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai.
224,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' mardon ki sab sey behtar saf pehli saf hai padhi. aur sab sey buri aakhiri saf aur aurton ki sab sey behtar saf aakhiri saf padhi. hai aur sab sey buri pehli saf '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is bab mein Jabir , ibne-Abbas , abu-Saeed , Ubai-bin Kaab , Aaisha , Arbaz bin Saariya aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey ye bhi marvi hai ke aap pehli saf walon key liye teen baar istighfar kartey they aur dusri key liye eik baar ."
225,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' agar logon ko malum ho jaey ke Azan aur pehli saf mein kya sawab hai, aur wo usey qura andazi key baghair na paa saktey hon to uskey liye qura andazi kartey ''."
226,Malik sey isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki hai.
227,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamari safen sidhi kartey they. chunanche eik din aap nikley to dekha ke eik shakhs ka Sina logon sey aagey nikla huwa hai, aap ney farmaya : '' tum apni safen sidhi rakho padhi. aur na Allah tumharey darmiyan ikhtilaf paida farma dega '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is bab mein Jabir bin Samra, Bara, Jabir bin Abdullah , Anas , Abu-Hurera aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi hai ke aap ney farmaya : safein sidhi karna namaz ki takmil hai, 4- umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai ke wo safen sidhi karney ka kaam kuch logon key supurd kar detey they to muazzan us waqt tak iqaamat nahin kehta jab tak usey ye na bata diya jata ke safen sidhi ho chuki hain, 5- Ali aur Usman Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi marvi hai ke ye dono bhi uski pabandi kartey they aur kehtey they : « استووا » '' saf mein sidhey ho jao '' aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they : falan ! aagey badho, falan ! peechey hato ."
228,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey jo samajhdaar hon in ko mujh sey qarib rehna chahiye, phir wo jo ( aql o danish mein) unkey qarib hon , phir wo jo unkey qarib hon , tum aagey peechey na hona ke tumharey dilon mein phoot pad jaeygi, aur apney aap ko bazar key shor o ghogha sey bachaey rakhna''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ubai-bin Kaab, abu-Masood, abu-Saeed, Bara , aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. - Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai ke aap is baat sey khush hotey ke muhajrin aur ansaar aapas mein qarib qarib rahen taake wo aap sey) seekhey huye masaayel ( mehfooz rakh saken ."
229,"hamney umra mein sey eik ameer key peechey namaz padhi , logon ney hamen do sutonon key darmiyan namaz padhney par majbur kar diya padhi. jab hum namaz padh chukey to Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein us sey bachtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is bab mein Qura bin Ayas muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ulama mein sey kuch logon ney sutonon key darmiyan saf laganey ko makrooh jana hai. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain, aur ulama kuch ney uski ijazat di hai padhi. ."
230,"Ziyad bin abi al-Jaad ney mera haath pakda , ( hum log Riqa mein they ( phir unhoney mujhey ley ja kar bani Asad key Wabsa bin Maabad naami eik Shekh key paas khada kya aur kaha : mujh sey us Shekh ney bayan kya aur Shekh un ki baat sun rahey they ke eik shakhs ney saf key peechey tanha namaz padhi to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey salaat dohraaney ka hukm diya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Wabsa bin Maabad (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- is bab mein Ali bin Sheban aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- ehle-ilm mein sey kuch logon ney makrooh samjha hai ke aadmi saf key peechey tanha namaz padhey aur kaha hai ke agar usney saf key peechey tanha namaz padhi hai to wo namaz dohraaey , yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain, 4- ehle-ilm mein sey baaz logon ney kaha hai ke usey kafi hoga jab wo saf key peechey tanha namaz padhey, Sufiyan Sory, ibne-Mubarak aur Shafai ka bhi yehi qol hai, 5- ehle-koofa mein sey kuch log Wabsa bin Maabad ki hadees ki taraf gaey hain, un logon ka kehna hai ke jo saf key peechey tanha namaz padhey , wo usey dohraaey . unhi mein sey Hammad bin abi Suleman (Alaihissalam) , ibne-Abi Leila aur Wakee hain, 6- muallif ney is hadees key turq key zikr key baad farmaya ke Amr bin Murra ki hadees jisey unhoney b-tareeq « Hilal bin Yusaf, an Amr bin Rashid, an Wabsa» riwayat ki hai, ziyada sahih hai, aur baaz ney kaha hai ke Husain ki hadees jisey unhoney b-tareeq «Hilal bin Yusaf, an Ziyad bin abi al-Jaad an Wabisa» riwayat ki hai ziyada sahih hai. aur merey nazdik ye Amr bin Murra ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, isliye ke ye Hilal bin Yusaf key ilawa tareeq sey bhi Ziyad bin abi al-Jaad key wastey sey Wabsa sey marvi hai."
231,Wabsa bin Maabad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ney saf key peechey akeley namaz padhi to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey namaz dohraaney ka hukm diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Wakee kehtey hain ke jab aadmi saf key peechey akeley namaz padhey to wo namaz ko dohraaey ( uski namaz nahin hui )۔
232,"eik raat mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath namaz padhi , main ja kar aap key baain janib khada ho gaya to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney peechey sey mera sar pakda aur mujhey apney daain taraf kar liya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is bab mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadees aai hai, 3- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad waley ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke jab eik aadmi Imam key sath ho to wo Imam key daain janib khada ho."
233,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen hukm diya ke jab hum teen hon to hum mein sey eik aagey badh jaey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Jabir aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai ke jab teen aadmi hon to do aadmi Imam key peechey khadey hon, ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney Alqama aur Aswad ko namaz padhaai to un dono mein sey eik ko apney daain taraf aur doosrey ko baain taraf khada kya aur ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) usey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kya, 4- baaz logon ney Ismail bin Muslim makki par unkey hifz key talluq sey kalam kya hai."
234,"un ki daadi Muleka (Raziallahu Anha) ney khana pakaya aur us ko khaney key liye Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko madoo kya, aap ney is mein sey khaya phir farmaya : ''utho chalo hum tumhen namaz padhaein'' , Anas kehtey hain padhi. : to main uth kar apni eik chataai key paas aaya jo ziyada istimal ki wajeh sey kaali ho gaee thi, mainey usey pani sey dhoya , phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam is par khadey huye, mainey aur yatim ney aap key peechey is par saf lagai aur daadi hamarey peechey khadi huin, to aap ney hamen do rakaat padhaain , phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamari taraf paltey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke jab Imam key sath eik mard aur eik aurat ho to mard Imam key daain taraf khada ho aur aurat un dono key peechey . 3- baaz logon ney is hadees sey daleel li hai ke jab aadmi saf key peechey tanha ho to uski namaz jayez hai, wo kehtey hain ke bachey par namaz to thi hi nahin goya amalan Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key peechey tanha hi they, lekin un ki ye daleel sahih nahin hai kyonkey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Anas ko apney peechey yatim key sath khada kya tha, aur agar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam yatim ki namaz ko namaz na mantey to yatim ko unkey sath khada na kartey balke Anas ko apney daain taraf khada kartey , Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath namaz padhi to aap ney unhen apni daain taraf khada kya, is hadees mein daleel hai ke aap ney nafl namaz padhi thi aur unhen barkat pahunchaney ka irada kya tha."
235,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' logon ki imaamat wo karey jo Allah ki kitab ( Quran (ka sab sey ziyada ilm rakhney wala ho, agar log Quran key ilm mein barabar hon to jo sab sey ziyada sunnat ka janney wala ho wo imaamat karey , aur agar wo sunnat key ilm mein bhi barabar hon to jisney sab sey pehley hijrat ki ho wo imaamat karey , agar wo hijrat mein bhi barabar hon to jo umr mein sab sey bada ho wo imaamat karey , aadmi key daayra iqtidar mein uski imaamat na ki jaey aur na kisi aadmi key ghar mein uski makhsus jagah par uski ijazat key baghair betha jaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is bab mein abu-Saeed , Anas bin Malik , Malik bin Huweris aur Amr bin Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aur ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, unka kehna hai ke logon mein imaamat ka haqdaar wo hai jo Allah ki kitab ( Quran (aur sunnat ka sab sey ziyada ilm rakhta ho. neez wo kehtey hain ke ghar ka Malik khud imaamat ka ziyada mustahiq hai, aur baaz ney kaha hai : jab ghar ka Malik kisi doosrey ko ijazat dedey to uskey namaz padhaaney mein koi harj nahin, lekin baaz logon ney isey bhi makrooh jana hai, wo kehtey hain ke sunnat yehi hai ke ghar ka Malik khud padhaaey padhi. , 4- Ahmed bin Hanbal Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key farman : '' aadmi key daayra iqtidar mein uski imaamat na ki jaey aur na uskey ghar mein uski makhsus nashist par uski ijazat key baghair betha jaey '' key barey mein kehtey hain ke jab wo ijazat dedey to main ummid rakhta hun ke ye ijazat musnad par bethney aur imaamat karney dono sey mutalliq hogi, unhoney uskey namaz padhaaney mein koi harj nahin jana ke jab wo ijazat dedey."
236,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi logon ki imaamat karey to chaahiye ke halki namaz padhaaey , kyonkey un mein chhotey , badey , kamzor aur bimar sabhi hotey hain aur jab wo tanha namaz padhey to jaisey chahey padhey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is bab mein Adi bin Hatim , Anas , Jabir bin Samra , Malik bin Abdullah , abu Waqid , Usman , abu-Masood , Jabir bin Abdullah aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- yehi aksar ehle-ilm ka qol hai, un logon ney usi ko pasand kya ke Imam namaz lambi na padhaaey taake kamzor , boodhey aur bimar logon ko pareshani na ho."
237,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam logon mein sab sey ziyada halki aur sab sey zyada mukammal namaz padhney waley they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
238,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' namaz ki kunji wuzu ( tahaarat ( hai, uski Tehreem takbir hai aur uski tahleel salam pherna hai, aur us aadmi ki namaz hi nahin jo « Alhamdulillah » ( Sura Fatiha (aur uskey sath koi aur Sura na padhey chahey farz namaz ho ya koi aur namaz ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- is bab mein Ali aur Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees sanad key aetbar sey sab sey umda aur abu Saeed Khudri ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, hum usey kitabul wuzu key shuru mein zikr kar chukey hain ( hadees number : padhi. ( , 4- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai, yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain ke namaz ki Tehreem takbir hai, aadmi namaz mein takbir key ( yani Allahu-akbar kahey ( baghair dakhil nahin ho sakta , 5- Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi kehtey hain : agar aadmi Allah key namon mein sey 70 naam ley kar namaz shuru karey aur '' Allahu-akbar '' na kahey to bhi ye usey kafi na hoga . aur agar salam pherney sey pehley usey hadas laahiq ho jaey to main usey hukm deta hun ke wuzu karey phir apni ( namaz ki) jagah aa kar bethey aur salam pherey , aur hukm ( Rasool (apney haal ( zahir ( par) baqi ( rahega padhi. ."
239,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab namaz key liye Allahu-akbar kehtey to apni ungliyan khuli rakhtey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- deegar kaee logon ney ye hadees b-tareeq « ibne-Abi Zi-ib an Saeed bin Samaan an abi Hurera » riwayat ki hai) unkey alfaz hain (ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab namaz mein dakhil hotey to apney dono haath khub achi tarah uthatey they. ye riwayat Yahya bin Yamaan ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai, Yahya bin Yamaan ki riwayat ghalat hai un sey is hadees mein ghalati hui hai, ( uski wazahat aagey aa rahi hai )."
240,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab namaz key liye khadey hotey to apney dono haath khub achi tarah uthatey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman ( Darmi (ka kehna hai ke ye Yahya bin Yamaan ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, aur Yahya bin Yamaan ki hadees ghalat hai padhi. ."
241,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Allah ki raza key liye chaalis din tak takbire-oola key sath ba-jamaat namaz padhi to uskey liye do qism ki bara-at likhi jaeygi : eik aag sey bara-at , dusri nifaq sey bara-at ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Anas sey ye hadees moqufan bhi riwayat ki gaee hai, aur hum nahin jantey ke abu-Quteba Salma bin Quteba key siwa kisi ney isey marfoo riwayat kya ho ye hadees Habib bin abi Habib bijli sey bhi riwayat ki jati hai unhoney usey Anas bin Malik sey riwayat kya hai aur usey Anas hi ka qol qarar diya hai, usey marfoo nahin kya, neez Ismail bin Ayash ney ye hadees b-tareeq « imarat bin Ghazia an Anas bin maalik an umr bin Khattab an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » isi tarah riwayat ki hai, aur ye hadees ghair mehfooz aur mursal padhi. hai, Imaara bin ghaziya ney Anas bin Malik ka zamana nahin paya ."
242,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam raat ko jab namaz key liye khadey hotey to (Allah akbar) kehtey , phir « سبحانك اللهم وبحمدك وتبارك اسمك وتعالى جدك wala إله غيرك » ''aey Allah! pak hai to har aeb aur har naqs sey , sab taarifein terey liye hain, ba-barkat hai tera naam aur buland hai teri shaan , aur terey siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin '' padhtey phir « الله أكبر كبيرا » '' Allah bahut bada hai'' kehtey phir أعوذ باهلل السميع العليم من الشيطان الرجيم من همزه ونفخه ونفثه ''main Allah samee o aleem ki shetan mardud sey, panah chahta hun, uskey waswason sey, uskey kibr o nakhwat sey aur uskey Ashaar aur jadu sey'' kehtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali , Aaisha , Abdullah bin Masood , Jabir , Juber bin Mut-im aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- is bab mein abu-Saeed ki hadees sab sey ziyada mashhoor hai, 3- ehle-ilm mein sey kuch logon ney usi hadees ko ikhtiyar kya hai, rahey aksar ehle-ilm to un logon ney wohi kaha hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai ke aap « سبحانك اللهم وبحمدك وتبارك اسمك وتعالى جدك wala إله غيرك » kehtey they padhi. aur isi tarah umr bin khattab aur Abdullah bin Masood Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai. Tabe-een waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 4- abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ki sanad mein kalam kya gaya hai. Yahya bin Saeed Raavi hadees Ali bin Ali Rifaai key barey mein kalam kartey they. aur Ahmed kehtey they ke ye hadees sahih nahin hai."
243,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab namaz shuru kartey to « سبحانك اللهم وبحمدك وتبارك اسمك وتعالى جدك wala إله غيرك » kehtey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- Harisa key hifz key talluq sey kalam kya gaya hai."
244,"merey walid ney mujhey namaz mein «Bismillahirrehmanirraheem» kehtey suna to unhoney mujh sey kaha : betey ! ye bidat hai, aur bidat sey bacho. mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key as-haab mein sey kisi ko nahin dekha jo un sey ziyada Islam mein bidat ka mukhalif ho, mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath , abu-Bakar key sath , umr key sath aur Usman (Raziallauh anhum) key sath namaz padhi hai lekin mainey un mein sey kisi ko usey ( oonchi aawaz sey) kehtey nahin suna , to tum bhi usey na kaho padhi. , jab tum namaz padho to qirat ""Al-hamdulillahi rabbil-aalameen» sey shuru karo . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- Sahaba jin mein abu-Bakar, Umar, Usman, Ali Raziallahu anhum waghera shamil hain aur unkey baad key Tabe-een mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai, aur yehi Sufiyan Sory, ibne-Mubarak, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain, ye log « Bismillahirrehmanirrahim» zor sey kehney ko durust nahin samajhtey ( balke ( unka kehna hai ke aadmi usey apney dil mein kahey padhi. ."
245,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni namaz « بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم » sey shuru kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- iski sanad qawi nahin hai, 2- Sahaba kiram mein sey jin mein Abu-Hurera , ibne-Umar , ibne-Abbas aur ibn Zuber (Raziallauh anhum) shamil hain aur unkey baad Tabe-een mein sey kaee ehle-ilm « بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم » zor sey kehney key qaail hain, aur yehi Shafai bhi kehtey hain."
246,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam , abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallauh anhum) « Al-hamdulillahi rabbil aalamin » sey qirat shuru kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Sahaba kiram , Tabe-een aur unkey baad key logon mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log « Al-hamdulillahi rabbil aalamin » sey qirat shuru kartey they. Shafai kehtey hain ke '' Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam , abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallauh anhum) « Al-hamdulillahi rabbil aalamin » sey qirat shuru kartey they '' ka matlab ye hai ke ye log sura sey pehley Sura Fatiha padhtey they, uska ye matlab nahin ke wo « بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم » nahin padhtey they, Shafai ki raey hai ke qirat « بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم » sey shuru ki jaey aur usey buland aawaz sey padha jaey jab qirat aawaz sey ki jaey padhi. ."
247,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' uski namaz nahin jisney Sura Fatiha nahin padhi '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ubada bin Samit ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Aaisha , Anas , abu-Qatada aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Sahaba kiram mein sey aksar ehle-ilm jin mein umr bin Khattab , Ali bin abi Talib , Jabir bin Abdullah aur Imran bin Husain waghaira (Raziallauh anhum) shamil hain ka isi par amal hai. un logon ka kehna hai ke Sura Fatiha padhey baghair namaz kifaayat nahin karti , Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : jis namaz mein Sura Fatiha nahin padhi gaee wo naqis aur na-mukammal hai. yehi ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain."
248,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko « غير المغضوب عليهم wala الضالين » padh kar , Aameen kehtey suna , aur uskey sath aap ney apni aawaz khinchi ( yani buland ki) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- is bab mein Ali aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Sahaba Tabe-een aur unkey baad key logon mein sey kaee ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai ke aadmi Aameen kehney main apni aawaz buland karey usey past na rakhey. Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain. ( شاذ ( 4- Shoba ney ye hadees b-tareeq «سلمة بن كهيل، an حُجر أبي العنبس، an Alqama بن وائل، an Abeeh وائل» riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney « غير المغضوب عليهم wala الضالين » padha to aap ney Aameen kahi aur apni aawaz past ki, 5- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke Sufiyan ki hadees Shoba ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. Shoba ney is hadees mein kaee maqamat par ghaltiyaan ki hain padhi. unhoney Hajar abi Anbas kaha hai, jabke wo Hajar bin Anbas hain aur un ki kunniyat abul-Sakan hai aur is mein unhoney « an Alqama bin Wayl » ka wasta badha diya hai jabke is mein Alqama ka wasta nahin hai, Hajar bin Anbas barahe-rast Hajar sey riwayat kar rahey hain, aur « وخفض بها صوته » ( aawaz past ki) kaha hai, jabke ye « ومدّ بها صوته » ( apni aawaz khinchi ( hai, 6- mainey abu-Zara'a sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : Sufiyan ki hadees Shoba ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. aur Alaa bin Saleh Asadii ney bhi Salma bin kuheil sey Sufiyan hi ki hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai padhi. ."
249,"Wayl Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey Sufiyan ki) pichli ( riwayat jaisi riwayat hai,"
250,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab Imam Aameen kahey to tum log bhi Aameen kaho. isliye ke jiski Aameen farishton ki Aameen sey mil gaee to uskey pichley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai.
251,"( namaz mein) do saktey hain jinhen mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey yad kya hai, is par Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ney uska inkar kya aur kaha : hamen to eik hi sakta yad hai. chunanche ( Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ( hamney Madiney mein Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ko likha , to unhoney likha ke Samra ney ( theek ( yad rakha hai. Saeed bin abi Aruba kehtey hain : to hamney Qatada sey puchha : ye do saktey kon-kon sey hain? unhoney kaha : jab namaz mein dakhil hotey (pehla us waqt) aur jab aap qirat sey farigh hotey, phir uskey baad kaha aur jab « wala الضالين » kehtey padhi. aur aap ko ye baat achi lagti thi ke jab aap qirat sey farigh hon to thodi der chup rahen yahan tak ke saans thehar jaey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadees aai hai, 3- ehle-ilm mein sey bahut sey logon ka yehi qol hai ke wo Imam key liye namaz shuru karney key baad aur qirat sey farigh honey key baad) thodi der ( chup rehney ko mustahab jantey hain. aur yehi Ahmed , Is-haq bin Raahviya aur hamarey as-haab bhi kehtey hain."
252,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamari imaamat kartey to baaein hath ko apney daain haath sey pakadtey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Halab (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- is bab mein Wayl bin Hajar , Ghutef bin Haris , ibne-Abbas , ibne-Masood aur Suhel bin Saad (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Sahaba kiram , Tabe-een aur unkey baad key ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai ke aadmi namaz mein dahina hath baaein hath par rakhey padhi. , aur baaz ki raey hai ke unhen naaf key ooper rakhey aur baaz ki raey hai ke naaf key nichey rakhey , unkey nazdik un sab ki gunjaaish hai."
253,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam har jhukney , uthney , khadey honey aur bethney key waqt Allahu-akbar kehtey padhi. aur abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma bhi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Anas , ibne-Umar , abu Malik Ash-ari , abu-Musa , Imran bin Husain , Wayl bin Hajar aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Sahaba kiram ka jin mein abu-Bakar , umr , Usman Ali (Raziallauh anhum) waghera shamil hain aur unkey baad key Tabe-een ka amal usi par hai aur usi par aksar fuqaha o ulama ka amal bhi hai."
254,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jhuktey waqt « الله أكبر » kehtey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key Tabe-een mein sey ehle-ilm ka qol yehi hai ke rukoo aur sajda key liye jhuktey huye aadmi « الله أكبر » kahey."
255,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha ke jab aap namaz shuru kartey to apney dono haath uthatey yahan tak ke unhen apney dono kandhon key bilmuqaabil kartey , aur jab rukoo kartey aur rukoo sey apna sar uthatey ( to bhi isi tarah dono haath uthatey ( padhi. . ibne-Abi umr ( Tirmizi key doosrey ustad ( ney apni riwayat mein ye izafa kya hai, dono sajdon key darmiyan nahin uthatey they."
256,"Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Ali , Wayl bin Hajar , Malik bin Huweris , Anas , Abu-Hurera , abu-Humed , abu-Usaid , Sehal bin Saad , Muhammad bin Muslima , abu-Qatada , abu-Musa Ash-ari , Jabir aur Umer Leisi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- yehi Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm jin mein ibne-Umar , Jabir bin Abdullah , Abu-Hurera , Anas , ibne-Abbas , Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallauh anhum) waghera shamil hain aur Tabe-een mein sey Hasan Basri , Ata , Taaus , Mujahid , Nafey , Salim bin Abdullah , Saeed bin Juber waghera kehtey hain, aur yehi Malik , Maamar , Auzaai , ibn Uena , Abdullah bin Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain, 4- Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain : jo apney dono haath uthatey hain un ki hadees ( daleel ( sahih hai, phir unhoney b-tareeq Zohri riwayat ki hai, 5- aur ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees '' Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney sirf pehli martaba apney dono haath uthaey '' wali Sabit nahin hai, 6- Malik bin Anas namaz mein rafaa-yadein ko sahih samajhtey they, 7- abdur-Razzaaq ka bayan hai ke Maamar bhi namaz mein rafaa-yadein ko sahih samajhtey they, 8- aur mainey Jarood bin Muaz ko kehtey suna ke '' Sufiyan bin Uena , umr bin Harun aur Nazar bin Shumeil apney haath uthatey jab namaz shuru kartey aur jab rukoo kartey aur jab rukoo sey apna sar uthatey ''."
257,"Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : '' kya main tumhen Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki tarah namaz na padhaaun ? to unhoney namaz padhaai aur sirf pehli martaba apney dono haath uthaey padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadees aai hai, 3- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey bahut sey ehle-ilm yehi kehtey hain aur yehi Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka bhi qol hai."
258,"hum sey umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ghutnon ko pakadna tumharey liye masnoon kya gaya hai, lihaza tum ( rukoo mein) ghutney pakdey rakho . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saad , Anas , abu-Usaid , Sehal bin Saad , Muhammad bin Muslima aur abu-Masood (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Sahaba kiram , Tabe-een aur unkey baad key logon mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. is silsiley mein unkey darmiyan koi ikhtilaf nahin . siwaye uskey jo ibne-Masood aur unkey baaz shagirdon sey marvi hai ke wo log tatbeeq (yaksaniyat) padhi. kartey they, aur tatbeeq (yaksaniyat) ehle-ilm key nazdik mansookh hai."
259,hum log aisa kartey they ( yani tatbeeq (yaksaniyat) kartey they ( phir hamen is sey rok diya gaya aur hukm diya gaya ke hum hatheliyan ghutnon par rakhen .
260,"abu-Humed , abu-Usaid , Sehal bin Saad , aur Muhammad bin Muslima ( (Raziallauh anhum) ( chaaron ikhatta huye to un logon ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki namaz ka zikr kya, abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki namaz ko tum mein sab sey ziyada janta hun : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney rukoo kya to apney dono haath apney dono ghutnon par rakhey goya aap unhen pakdey huye hain, aur aap ney apney dono haathon ko kamaan ki taant ki tarah (tight) banaya aur unhen apney dono pehluon sey juda rakha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Humed ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- isi ko ehle-ilm ney ikhtiyar kya hai ke aadmi rukoo aur sajdey mein apney dono haathon ko apney dono pehluon sey juda rakhey."
261,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi rukoo karey to rukoo mein « subhana-rabbiyal-azeem » teen martaba kahey to uska rukoo pura ho gaya aur ye sab sey kam tadaad hai. aur jab sajda karey to apney sajdey mein teen martaba « subhan Rabbiyal-Aala » kahey to uska sajda pura ho gaya aur ye sab sey kam tadaad hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood ki hadees ki sanad muttasil nahin hai. Aun bin Abdullah bin Utba ki mulaqat ibne-Masood sey nahin hai padhi. , padhi. 2- is bab mein Huzefa aur Aqba bin Aamir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai, wo is baat ko mustahab samajhtey hain ke aadmi rukoo aur sajdey mein teen tasbeehaat sey kam na padhey , 4- Abdullah bin Mubarak sey marvi hai, unhoney kaha ke main Imam key liye mustahab samajhta hun ke wo paanch tasbeehaat padhey taake peechey waley logon ko teen tasbeehaat mil jaeyn aur isi tarah Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya ney bhi kaha hai."
262,unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath namaz padhi to aap apney rukoo mein « subhana-rabbiyal-azeem » aur sajdey mein « subhana-rabbiyal aala » padh rahey they. aur jab bhi rehmat ki kisi aayat par pahunchtey to thehertey aur sawal kartey aur jab azab ki kisi aayat par aatey to thehertey aur) azab sey) panah maangtey padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
263,"Shoba sey isi tarah marvi hai. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye hadees dusri sanadon sey bhi marvi hai ke unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath namaz tahajjud padhi , phir Raavi ney puri hadees zikr ki."
264,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney reshmi aur kusum key rangey huye kapdey pehanney , soney ki anguthi pehanney aur rukoo mein Quran padhney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram , Tabe-een padhi. aur unkey baad key logon mein sey ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai, un logon ney rukoo aur sajdey mein Quran padhney ko makrooh kaha hai."
265,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' us shakhs ki namaz kafi na hogi jo rukoo aur sajdey main apni peeth sidhi na rakhey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Masood Ansari ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali bin Sheban , Anas , Abu-Hurera aur Rifaa Zarqi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke aadmi rukoo aur sajdey main apni peeth sidhi rakhey , 4- Shafai , Ahmed , aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke jisney rukoo aur sajdey main apni peeth sidhi nahin rakhi to uski namaz faasid hai, isliye ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees hai : '' us shakhs ki namaz kafi na hogi jo rukoo aur sajdey main apni peeth sidhi na rakhey."
266,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab rukoo sey sar uthatey tu «سمع الله لمن حمده ربنا ولك الحمد ملء السموات وملء الأرض وملء ما بينهما وملء ما شئت من شيء بعد» ''Allah ney us shakhs ki baat sun li jisney uski tareef ki, aey hamarey rab ! tareef terey hi liye hai aasman bhar , zamin bhar , zamin o aasman ki tamam chizon bhar , aur uskey baad har us chiz bhar jo to chahey '' kehtey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , ibne-Abbas , ibne-Abi Aufi , abu-Hujefa aur abu-Saeed (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, aur yehi Shafai bhi kehtey hain ke farz ho ya nafl dono mein ye kalmaat kaheyga padhi. aur baaz ehle-koofa kehtey hain : ye sirf nafl namaz mein kaheyga . farz namaz mein usey nahin kahiyega."
267,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : jab Imam « samiallahu-liman hamida » '' Allah ney uski baat sun li jisney uski tareef ki '' kahey to tum « ربنا ولك الحمد » '' hamarey rab ! terey hi liye tamam tareefen hain'' kaho kyonkey jis ka qol farishton key qol key muwaafiq ho gaya to uskey guzishta gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai ke Imam «سمع الله لمن حمده ربنا ولك الحمد» kahey padhi. aur muqtadi « ربنا ولك الحمد » kahin , yehi Ahmed kehtey hain, 3- aur ibn Sirin waghera ka kehna hai jo Imam key peechey ( yani muqtadi (ho wo bhi «سمع الله لمن حمده ربنا ولك الحمد» isi tarah kaheyga padhi. jis tarah Imam kaheyga aur yehi Shafai aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain."
268,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha : jab aap sajda kartey to apney dono ghutney apney dono haath sey pehley rakhtey , aur jab uthtey to apney dono haath apney dono ghutnon sey pehley uthatey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum kisi ko nahin jantey jisney usey shareek sey is tarah riwayat kya ho, 2- aksar hal ilm key nazdik usi par amal hai, un ki raey hai ke aadmi apney dono ghutney apney dono haathon sey pehley rakhey aur jab uthey to apney dono haath apney dono ghutnon sey pehley uthaey , 3- hamaam ney Aasim padhi. sey usey mursalan riwayat kya hai. is mein unhoney Wayl bin Hajar ka zikr nahin kya."
269,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey koi ye qasd (irada) karta hai ke wo apni namaz mein oont key bethney ki tarah bethey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees gharib hai hum usey abu-Zinad ki hadees sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- ye hadees Abdullah bin Saeed Maqbari sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai, unhoney apney walid sey aur unkey walid ney Abu-Hurera sey aur Abu-Hurera ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. Abdullah bin Saeed Maqbari ko Yahya bin Saeed Qataan waghera ney zaeef qarar diya hai."
270,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab sajda kartey to apni naak aur peshani khub achi tarah zamin par jamatey, aur apney dono haathon ko apney dono pehluon sey door rakhtay, aur apni dono hatheliyon ko dono shaanon key bilmuqaabil rakhtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Humed ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas, Wayl bin Hajar aur abu-Saeed (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aur ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke aadmi apni peshani aur naak dono par sajda kerey. aur agar sirf peshani par sajda karey naak par na karey to ehle-ilm mein sey kuch logon ka kehna hai ke ye usey kafi hoga, aur kuch logon ka kehna hai ke kafi nahin hoga jab tak ke wo peshani aur naak dono par sajda na kerey."
271,"mainey Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab sajda kartey to apna chehra kahan rakhtey they? to unhoney kaha : apni dono hatheliyon key darmiyan. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Wayl bin Hajar aur abu-Humed Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aur usi ko baaz ehle-ilm ney ikhtiyar kya hai ke uskey dono haath uskey dono kanon key qarib hon۔"
272,"unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''jab banda sajda karta hai to uskey sath saat jod bhi sajda kartey hain : uska chehra padhi. uski dono hatheliyaan, uskey dono ghutney aur uskey dono qadam''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Abu-Hurera , Jabir aur abu-Saeed (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
273,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko hukm diya gaya ke aap saat aaza par sajda karen aur apney baal aur kapdey na sametein. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
274,"mein maqam namra key « Qaa » '' mistah zamin ''main apney walid key sath tha, to ( wahan sey) eik qafla guzra , kya dekhtey hain ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khadey namaz padh rahey hain, mein aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key dono baghlon ki safedi dekh raha tha jab aap sajda kartey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Aqram (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, usey hum sirf Dawud bin Qais ki sanad sey jantey hain. Abdullah bin Aqram Khuzai ki uskey ilawa koi aur hadees jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki ho hum nahin jantey , padhi. 2- Sahaba kiram mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai. aur Abdullah bin Arqam Zohri Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key as-haab mein sey hain aur wo abu-Bakar Siddiq key munshii they, padhi. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , ibne-Buhena , Jabir , Ahmar bin Juz, Memuna , abu-Humed , abu-Masood , abu-Usaid , Sehal bin Saad , Muhammad bin Muslima , Bara bin Aazib , Adi bin umaira aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- Ahmar bin juz Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key as-haab mein sey eik aadmi hain aur un ki sirf eik hadees hai."
275,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi sajda karey to aetidaal karey padhi. aur apney haath ko kuttey ki tarah na bichhaaey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdur-Rehman bin shabal , Anas , Bara , abu-Humed aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai, wo sajdey mein aetidaal ko pasand kartey hain aur haath ko darindey ki tarah bichaney ko makrooh samajhtey hain."
276,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' sajdey main apni haiyat darmiyani rakho , tum mein sey koi namaz mein apney dono haath kuttey ki tarah na bichhaaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
277,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney dono haathon ko) zamin par) rakhney aur dono paon ko khadey rakhney ka hukm diya hai.
278,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney dono haathon ko (zameen par) rakhney ka hukm diya hai, aagey Raavi ney isi tarah ki hadees zikr ki, albatta unhoney is mein « an abeeh» ka zikr nahin kya hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aamir bin Saad sey mursalan riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney dono haathon (zameen par) rakhney aur dono qadmon ko khadey rakhney ka hukm diya hai padhi. , 2- ye mursal riwayat wuhaib ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai padhi. , aur usi par ehle-ilm ka ijmaa' hai, aur logon ney usi ko ikhtiyar kya hai."
279,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab rukoo kartey, jab rukoo sey sar uthatey, jab sajda kartey aur jab sajda sey sar uthatey to aap ki namaz taqriban barabar barabar hoti thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadees hai."
280,"Hakam sey isi tarah marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur usi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai."
281,"hum jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key peechey namaz padhtey aur jab aap apna sar rukoo sey uthatey to hum mein sey koi bhi shakhs apni peeth ( sajdey key liye (us waqt tak nahin jhukaataa tha jab tak ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sajdey mein na chaley jatey , aap sajdey mein chaley jatey to hum sajda kartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas , Muawiya , ibne-Mas-ada sahab Juyush , aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aur yehi ehle-ilm kehtey hain yani : jo Imam key peechey ho wo un tamam umoor mein jinhen Imam kar raha ho Imam ki perwi karey , yani usey Imam key baad karey , Imam key rukoo mein janey key baad hi rukoo mein jaey aur uskey sar uthaney key baad hi apna sar uthaey , hamen us masley mein unkey darmiyan kisi ikhtilaf ka ilm nahin hai."
282,"mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aey Ali ! main tumharey liye wohi chiz pasand karta hun jo apney liye karta hun, aur wohi chiz napasand karta hun jo apney liye napasand karta hun. tum dono sajdon key darmiyan Iq-aa padhi. na karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hum usey Ali ki hadees sey sirf Abu-Is'haq Sabeei hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, unhoney Haris sey aur Haris ney Ali sey riwayat ki hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ney Haris al-Aur ko zaeef qarar diya hai padhi. , 3- is bab mein Aaisha , Anas aur Abu-Hurera sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- aksar ehle-ilm ka amal usi hadees par hai ke wo Iq-aa ko makrooh qarar detey hain."
283,"hamney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey dono qadmon par Iq-aa karney key silsiley mein puchha , to unhoney kaha : ye sunnat hai, to hamney kaha ke hum to usey aadmi ka phoohadpan samajhtey hain, unhoney kaha : nahin ye phoohadpan nahin hai balke ye tumharey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki sunnat hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- Sahaba kiram mein baaz ehle-ilm usi hadees ki taraf gaey hain, wo Iq-aa mein koi harj nahin jantey , Makka key baaz ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai, lekin aksar ehle-ilm dono sajdon key darmiyan Iq-aa ko napasand kartey hain padhi. ."
284,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam dono sajdon key darmiyan « اللهم اغفر لي وارحمني واجبرني واهدني وارزقني » '' aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey , mujh par reham farma , merey nuqsan ki talafi farma , mujhey hidayat dey aur mujhey rizq ata farma '' kehtey they padhi. ."
285,"kamil abul-Ula sey isi tarah marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, padhi. - isi tarah Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi marvi hai. aur baaz logon ney kamil abul-Ula sey ye hadees mursalan riwayat ki hai, 2- Shafai , Ahmed , Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain, un ki raey hai ke ye farz aur nafl dono mein jayez hai."
286,"baaz Sahaba ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sajdey mein dono haathon ko dono pehluon sey aur pet ko raan sey juda rakhney ki surat mein (takleef ki) shikayat ki, to aap ney farmaya : ghutnon sey (unpar tek laga kar) madad ley liya karo. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. hum sey abu-Saaleh ki hadees jisey unhoney Abu-Hurera sey aur Abu-Hurera ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai sirf usi tareeq sey (yani Les an ibn Ajlan ke tareeq sey) jantey hain aur Sufiyan bin Uena aur deegar kaee logon ney ye hadees  isi tarah  riwayat ki hai, un logon ki riwayat Les ki riwayat key muqabley mein shayad ziyada sahih hai."
287,"unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko namaz padhtey dekha , aap ki namaz is tarah sey thi ke jab aap taaq rakat mein hotey to us waqt tak nahin uthtey jab tak ke aap achchhi tarah beth na jatey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Malaik bin Huweris ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. aur yehi Is-haq bin Raahviya aur hamarey baaz as-haab (saathi) bhi kehtey hain."
288,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam namaz mein apney dono qadmon ke siron yani dono pairon ki ungliyon par zor dey kar uthtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ehle-ilm key nazdik Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hi ki hadees par amal hai. Khalid bin Ilyas muhaddeseen ke nazdik zaeef hain. unhen Khalid bin Ayas bhi kaha jata hai, log usi ko pasand kartey hain ke aadmi namaz mein apney dono qadmon ke siron par zor dey kar (baghair bethey) khada ho."
289,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein sikhaya ke jab hum do rakaaton ke baad bethein to ye dua padhen :(التحيات لله والصلوات والطيبات السلام عليك أيها النبي ورحمة الله وبركاته السلام علينا وعلى عباد الله الصالحين أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وأشهد أن محمدا عبده ورسوله).'' tamam  badani aur maali ibadaten Allah ke liye hain, salam ho aap par aey Nabi aur Allah ki rahmatein aur uski barkaten hon, salam ho hum par aur Allah ke nek bandon par, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees un sey kaee sanadon sey marvi hai, aur ye sab sey ziyada sahih hadees hai jo tashahud mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat hui hain. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Jabir , abu-Musa aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram unke baad Tabe-een mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 4- hum se Ahmed bin Muhammad bin Musa ne bayan kiya wo kehtey hain ke hamein Abdullah bin Mubarak ney khabar di, aur wo Maamar sey aur wo Khusaif sey riwayat kartey hain, Khusaif kehtey hain ke mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko khuwab mein dekha to mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! logon mein tashahud key silsiley mein ikhtilaf ho gaya hai? to aap ney farmaya : ''tum par ibne-Masood ka tashahud lazim hai.''"
290,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamein tashahud sikhatey jaisey aap hamein Quran sikhatey they aur farmatey : (التحيات المباركات الصلوات الطيبات لله سلام عليك أيها النبي ورحمة الله وبركاته سلام علينا وعلى عباد الله الصالحين أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وأشهد أن محمدا رسول الله ). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. 2- aur Abdur-Rehman bin Humaid ney bhi ye hadees abu-Zubair sey Les bin Saad ki hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai. 3- aur Aiman bin Makki ney ye hadees abu Zuber sey Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees sey riwayat ki hai aur ye ghair mehfooz hai. 4- Imam Shafai tashahud key silsiley mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees ki taraf gaey hain.
291,sunnat sey ye hai padhi. ke tashahud aahista padha jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- aur ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai.
292,"Main Madiney aaya to mainey (apney ji mein) kaha ke main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki namaz zarur dekhunga. (chunanche mainey dekha) jab aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tashahud key liye bethey to aap ney apna baayan pair bichhaya aur apna baayan haath apni baain raan par rakha aur apna daayan pair khada rakha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , ehle-koofa aur ibne-Mubarak ka bhi qol hai."
293,"Abu-Humed , Abu-Usaid , Sehal bin Saad aur Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallauh anhum) ikhattey huye, to un logon ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki namaz ka zikr kiya. is par abu-Humed kehney lagey ke main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki namaz ko tum mein sab sey ziyada janta hun, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tashahud key liye bethtey to aap apna baayan pair bichhate aur apney daain pair ki ungliyon ke siron ko qibley ki taraf mutawajjeh kartey, aur apni daahini hatheli dahiney ghutney par aur baain hatheli baain ghutney par rakhtay, aur apni ungli (shahadat ki ungli) sey ishara kartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- yehi baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain aur yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, ye log kehtey hain ke aakheer tashahud mein apney peeth par bethey , un logon ney abu-Humed ki hadees sey daleel pakdi hai. unka kehna hai ke pehley tashahud mein baain pair par bethey aur daayan pair khada rakhey."
294,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab namaz mein bethtey to apna daayan haath apney (daeyn) ghutney par rakhtey aur apney dahiney haath ke angoothey ke qarib wali ungli uthatey aur us sey dua kartey yani ishara kartey, aur apna baayan haath apney (baeyn) ghutney par phelaey rakhtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abdullah bin Zubair, Numer Khuzai , Abu-Hurera , abu-Humed aur Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 2- ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum usey Ubedullah bin umr ki hadees sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 3- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal tha, ye log tashahud mein ungli sey ishara karney ko pasand kartey aur yehi hamarey as-haab (saathiyon) ka bhi qol hai."
295,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney daain aur baeyn (السلام عليكم ورحمة الله السلام عليكم ورحمة الله) keh kar salam phertey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Saad bin abi Waqas , ibne-Umar , Jabir bin Samura , Bara , abu-Saeed , Ammar , Wayl bin Hajar , Adi bin Umaira aur Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram aur unke baad ke logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
296,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam namaz mein apney chehrey key samney daahini taraf thoda sa maael ho (jhuk) kar eik salam phertey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees hum sirf isi sanad sey marfoo jantey hain. 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : zuhair bin Muhammad sey ehale Sham munkir (buri) hadisein riwayat kartey hain. albatta unse marvi ehale iraaq ki riwaayatein ziyada sawaab wali aur ziyada sahih hain. 3- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke Ahmed bin Hanbal ka kehna hai ke shayad Zuhair bin Muhammad jo ehale Saam ke yahan gaey they, wo nahin jin sey Iraaq mein riwayat ki jati hai, koi doosrey aadmi hain jinka naam un logon ney badal diya hai, 4- is bab mein Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 5- namaz mein salam pherney key silsiley mein baaz ehle-ilm ney yehi kaha hai, lekin Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi sab sey sahih riwayat do salamon wali hai padhi. , Sahaba kiram , Tabe-een aur unke baad ke logon mein se aksar ehle-ilm usi ke qaail hain. albatta Sahaba kiram aur un ke ilawa mein sey kuchh logon ki raey hai ke farz namaz mein sirf eik salam hai, Shafai kehtey hain : chahey to sirf eik salam pherey aur chahey to do salam pherey."
297,(hazfe-salam) sunnat hai. Ali bin Hajar bayan kartey hain ke Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain : (hazfe-salam) ka matlab ye hai ke wo usey yani salam ko ziyada na kheenchey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- yehi hai jisey ehle-ilm mustahab jantey hain. 3- Ibrahim Nakhai sey marvi hai wo kehtey hain takbir juzam hai aur salam juzam hai (yani un dono mein mudd na kheenchey balke waqf karey).
298,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab salam phertey to (اللهم أنت السلام ومنك السلام تباركت ذا الجلال والإكرام). ''aey Allah to salam hai, tujh sey salamti hai, buzurgi aur izzat waley ! to badi barkat wala hai.'' kehney ke ba-qadr hi bethtey."
299,"Aasim  sey isi tarah ki hadees marvi hai aur is mein « تباركت يا ذا الجلال والإكرام » ( « ya » key sath ( hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, Khalid ney ye hadees ba-riwayat Aaisha Abdullah bin Haris sey Aasim ki hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai. 2- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi hai ke aap salam pherney key baad « لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد يحيي ويميت وهو على كل شيء قدير اللهم لا مانع لما أعطيت wala معطي لما منعت wala ينفع ذا الجد منك الجد».''Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, wo tanha hai, uska koi shareek nahin, badshahat usi ke liye hai aur tamam tareefen usi key liye hain, wohi zindagi aur maut deta hai, wo har chiz par qadir hai, aey Allah ! jo to dey usey koi rokney wala nahin aur jisey to na dey usey koi deney wala nahin, aur terey aagey kisi nasib waley ka koi nasib kaam nahin aata.'' kehtey they, ye bhi marvi hai ke aap «سبحان ربك رب العزة عما يصفون وسلام على المرسلين والحمد لله رب العالمين» ''paak hai tera rab jo izzat wala hai har us burai sey jo ye bayan kartey hain aur salamti ho Rasulon par aur tamam tareefen Allah key liye hain jo sarey jahan ka rab hai.'' bhi kehtey they. 3- is bab mein Soban , ibne-Umar , ibne-Abbas , abu-Saeed , Abu-Hurera aur Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
300,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab namaz sey (muqtadiyon ki taraf) palatney ka irada kartey to teen baar (استغفر الله) ''main Allah ki maghfirat chahta hun'' kehtey, phir (اللهم أنت السلام ومنك السلام تباركت يا ذا الجلال والإكرام) kehtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
301,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamari imaamat farmatey (to salam pherney key baad) apney dono taraf palat'tey they (kabhi) daain aur (kabhi) baeyn. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Halab (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood , Anas , Abdullah bin Amr , aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke Imam apney jis janib chahey palat kar bethey chahey to daain taraf aur chahey to baain taraf , Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey dono hi baaten sabit hain padhi. aur Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain agar aap ki zarurat daain taraf hoti to daain taraf palat'tey aur baain taraf hoti to baain taraf palat'tey."
302,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eik din masjid mein bethey huye they, hum bhi aap ke sath they, usi doran eik shakhs aap key paas aaya jo badwi lag raha tha, usney aa kar namaz padhi aur bahut jaldi jaldi padhi , phir palat kar aaya aur Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kiya to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''aur tum par bhi salam ho, wapis jaao phir sey namaz padho kyonkey tum ney namaz nahin padhi.'' to us shakhs ney wapis ja kar phir sey namaz padhi , phir wapis aaya aur aa kar usney aap ko salam kiya to aap ney phir farmaya : ''aur tumhen bhi salam ho, wapis jaao aur phir sey namaz padho kyonkey tum ney namaz nahin padhi.'' is tarah usne do baar ya teen baar kiya har baar wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key paas aa kar aap ko salam karta aur aap farmatey : ''tum par bhi salam ho, wapis jaao phir sey namaz padho kyonkey tum ney namaz nahin padhi.'' to log darey aur unpar ye baat giraan guzri ke jisney halki namaz padhi uski namaz hi nahin hui, aakhir us aadmi ney arz kiya, aap hamein (padh kar) dikha dijiye aur mujhey sikha dijiye , main insan hi to hun, main sahih bhi karta hun aur mujh sey ghalati bhi ho jati hai, to aap ney farmaya : ''jab tum namaz key liye khadey honey ka irada karo to pehley wuzu karo jaisey Allah ney tumhen wuzu karney ka hukm diya hai, phir Azan do aur takbir kaho aur agar tumhen kuchh Quran yad ho to usey padho warna «الحمد لله » ، padhi. « الله أكبر » aur « لا إله إلا الله » kaho , phir rukoo mein jaao aur khub itminan sey rukoo karo, uskey baad bilkul sidhey khadey ho jaao , phir sajda karo, aur khub aetidaal sey sajda karo, phir betho aur khub itminan sey betho , phir utho , jab tum ney aisa kar liya to tumhari namaz puri ho gaee aur agar tum ney is mein kuchh kami ki to tum ney itni hi apni namaz mein sey kami ki .''  Raavi (Rifaa) kehtey hain : to ye baat unhen pehley sey aasan lagi ke jisney is mein sey kuchh kami ki to usney itni hi apni namaz sey kami ki, puri namaz nahin gaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Rifaa bin Raafey ki hadees Hasan hai, Rifaa sey ye hadees dusri sanad sey bhi riwayet hui hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
303,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein dakhil huye itney main eik aur shakhs bhi dakhil huwa , usney namaz padhi phir aa kar Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kiya to aap ney uskey salam ka jawab diya aur farmaya : '' tum wapis jao aur phir sey namaz padho , kyonkey tum ney namaz nahin padhi. ''  chunanche aadmi ney wapis ja kar namaz padhi , jaisey pehley padhi thi, phir Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key paas aa kar aap ko salam kiya to aap ney salam ka jawab diya aur farmaya : '' wapis jao aur phir sey namaz padho , kyonkey tum ney namaz nahin padhi.'' yahan tak usney teen baar aisa kiya, phir us aadmi ney arz kiya : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq key sath mab-us farmaya (bheja hai) main is sey behtar nahin padh sakta. lihaza aap mujhey namaz padhna sikha dijiye. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' tum jab namaz ka irada karo to (Allah akbar) kaho phir jo tumhen Quran mein sey yad ho padho , phir rukoo karo yahan tak ke rukoo ki haalat main tumhen khub itminan ho jaey, phir sar uthao yahan tak ke achchhi tarah khadey ho jao , phir sajda karo yahan tak ke khub itminan sey sajda kar lo , phir sar uthao yahan tak ke itminan sey beth jao aur isi tarah sey apni puri namaz mein karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ibne Numer ney Ubedullah bin umr sey isi sanad sey riwayat ki hai lekin «an Abiy» se nahin zikr kiya hai. 3- Yahya Al Qattan ki riwayat mein « Abdullah bin umr an Saeed bin Ubai Al Maqbari an Abiy an Ubai Huraira» hai, aur ye ziyada sahih hai."
304,"Unhoney abu Humed Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey hain suna ( jab ( Sahaba kiram mein sey das logon key sath they, un mein sey eik abu-Qatada bin Rabaee they, abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) keh rahey they ke main tum mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki namaz ka sab sey ziyada jaan-kaar hun, to logon ney kaha ke tumhen na to hum sey pehley sohbate Rasool muyassar hui aur na hi tum hum sey ziyada Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key paas aatey jatey they? to unhoney kaha : haan ye theek hai (lekin mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka tariqa namaz ziyada yad hai) is par logon ney kaha (agar tum ziyada jantey ho) to pesh karo, to unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab namaz key liye khadey hotey to bilkul sidhey khadey ho jatey aur apney dono haath uthatey yahan tak ke unhen apney dono mundhon key muqabil mein ley jatey , phir jab rukoo ka irada kartey to apney dono haath uthatey yahan tak ke unhen apney dono mundhon key muqabil mein ley jatey , phir « الله أكبر » kehtey aur rukoo kartey aur bilkul sidhey ho jatey , na apna sar bilkul nichey jhukaatey aur na ooper hi uthaey rakhtey aur apney dono haath apney dono ghutnon par rakhtey , phir « samiallahu-liman hamida » kehtey aur apney dono haath uthatey (yani rafaa-yadein kartey) aur sidhey khadey ho jatey yahan tak ke jism ki har eik haddi sidhi ho kar apni jagah par lot aati phir sajda karney key liye zamin ki taraf jhuktey , phir « الله أكبر » kehtey aur apney baazuoon ko apni dono baghal sey juda rakhtey , aur apney pairon ki ungliyan khuli rakhtey , phir apna baayan pair modtey aur is par bethtey aur sidhey ho jatey yahan tak ke har haddi apni jagah par lot aati, aur aap uthtey aur dusri rakat mein bhi isi tarah kartey yahan tak ke dusri rakat sey jab (teesri rakat key liye) uthtey to «الله أكبر » kehtey aur apney dono haath uthatey yahan tak ke unhen apney dono mundhon key muqabil mein kartey jaisey us waqt kiya tha jab aap ney namaz shuru ki thi, phir isi tarah kartey yahan tak ke jab wo rakat hoti jis mein namaz khatam ho rahi ho to apna baayan pair muakhkhar (peechhe) kartey yani usey daahini taraf daain pair ke nichey sey nikal letey aur peeth par bethtey, phir salam phertey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur unke qol « رفع يديه إذا قام من السجدتين » ''dono sajdon sey khadey hotey waqt apney dono haath uthatey'' ka matlab hai ke jab do rakaaton ke baad (teesri rakat key liye) khadey hotey."
305,"Mainey Abu Humed Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ko das Sahaba kiram ki mojudgi mein jin mein abu-Qatada bin Rabaee bhi they, kehtey suna , phir unhoney Yahya bin Saeed ki hadees ki tarah usi mafhoom ki hadees zikr ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees mein abu-Aasim Zuhaak bin Mukhlid ney Abdul-Humed bin Jaafar ke wastey sey is lafz ka izafa kiya hai ke (nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki namaz wali us sift aur kaifiyat ko sun-ney waley) Sahaba kiram (Raziallauh anhum) ajmaeen ney kaha ke aap ney sahih kaha , Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isi tarah namaz padhtey they."
306,"mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Fajr mein pehli rakat mein « والنخل باسقات » (sura Qaaf) padhtey suna padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Qutba bin Malik ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Amr bin Hurais, Jabir bin Samura , Abdullah bin Saaib , abu-Barza aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney Fajr mein Sura (الواقعہ) padhi.  4- ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap Fajr mein saath (60) sey ley kar so (100) aayaten padha kartey they.  5- aur ye bhi marvi hai ke aap ney (إذا الشمس كورت) padhi. 6- aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney abu-Musa Ash-ari ko likha ke Fajr mein tawaal mufassal (Sura Qaaf se Sura Burooj tak) padha karo. 7- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak aur Shafai ka qol hai."
307,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar aur Asr mein (وسماء ذات البروج), (والسماء والطارق) aur in jaisi suraten padha kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Khubab , abu-Saeed , abu-Qatada , Zaid bin Sabit aur Bara bin Aazib (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney Zohar mein (الم تنزیل) yani Sura Sajda key ba-qadr qirat ki. 4- ye bhi marvi  hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki pehli rakat mein tees aayaton ke ba-qadr aur dusri rakat mein pandarah aayaton ke ba-qadr qirat kartey they. 5-  umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko likha ke tum Zohar mein (wasaat mufassal) (Sura Burooj se Sura Bayyana tak)padha karo.  6- baaz ehle-ilm ki raey hai ke Asr ki qirat maghrib ki qirat ki tarah hogi, un mein  (Imam) (qasaar mufassal) (Sura Bayyana se aakheer tak ke beech se) padheyga. 7- aur Ibrahim Nakhai kehtey hain ke Zohar ki qirat Asr ki qirat sey chaar guna hogi."
308,"Unki maa Umme Fazal (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamari taraf is haal mein nikley ke aap bimari mein apney sar par patti baandhey huye they, maghrib padhaai to Sura ''مرسلات'' padhi , phir uskey baad aap ney ye sura nahin padhi yahan tak ke aap Allah sey ja miley. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Umme Fazal ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Juber bin Mut-im , ibne-Umar , abu-Ayyub aur Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney maghrib mein dono rakaaton mein Sura ''الاعراف'' padhi , aur aap sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney maghrib mein Sura ''الطور'' padhi. 5- umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko likha ke tum maghrib mein (qasaar mufassal) (Sura Bayyana se aakheer tak ke beech se) padha karo. 6- aur abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai ke wo maghrib mein (qasaar mufassal) (Sura Bayyana se aakheer tak ke beech se) padhtey they. 7- ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai. ibne-Mubarak , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain. 8- Imam Shafai kehtey hain ke Imam Malik key silsiley mein zikr kiya gaya hai ke unhoney maghrib mein Sura taur aur Mursalat jaisi lambi suraten padhney ko makrooh jana hai. Shafai kehtey hain : lekin main makrooh nahin samajhta , balke maghrib mein un Suraton key padhey janey ko mustahab samajhta hun."
309,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Isha mein (والشمس وضحاها) aur us jaisi suraten padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Barida (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Bara bin Aazib aur Anas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey marvi hai ke aap ney Isha mein Sura (والتين والزيتون) padhi 4- Usman bin Affaan sey marvi hai ke wo Isha mein  (wasaat mufassal) ki suraten jaisey Sura ''المنافقون'' aur us jaisi dusri suraten padha kartey they, 5- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een sey ye bhi marvi hai ke un logon ney us sey ziyada aur us sey kam bhi padhi hai. goya unkey nazdik mamley mein wusat hai lekin is silsiley mein sab sey behtar chiz jo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey marvi hai wo ye ke aap ney Sura (والشمس وضحاها) aur Sura (والتين والزيتون) padhi."
310,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney Isha mein Sura « والتين والزيتون » padhi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
311,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney Fajr padhi , aap par qirat dushwaar ho gaee , namaz sey farigh honey key baad aap ney farmaya : '' mujhey lag raha hai ke tum log apney Imam key peechhey qirat kartey ho?'' hamney arz kiya : ji haan , Allah ki qism hum qirat kartey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''tum aisa na kiya karo siwaye Sura Fatiha key isliye ke jo usey nahin padhta uski namaz nahin hoti hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- ye hadees Zohri ney bhi Mehmood bin Rabee sey aur Mehmood ney Ubada bin Samit sey aur Ubada ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey riwayat ki hai. aap ney farmaya is shakhs ki namaz nahin jisney Sura Fatiha nahin padhi , ye sab sey sahih riwayat hai, 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Aaisha , Anas , abu-Qatada aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- Sahaba aur Tabe-een mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka Imam key peechey qirat key silsiley mein amal isi hadees par hai. Aaimma kiram mein sey Malik bin Anas , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol bhi yehi hai, ye sabhi log Imam key peechhey qirat key qaail hain."
312,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney us namaz sey farigh honey key baad jis mein aap ney buland aawaz sey qirat ki thi to farmaya : '' kya tum mein sey abhi kisi ney merey sath qirat ki hai? '' eik shakhs ney arz kya : ji haan Allah key Rasool ! ( mainey ki hai) aap ney farmaya : '' tabhi to main ye keh raha tha : aakhir kya baat hai ke Quran ki qirat mein meri aawaz sey aawaz takrai ja rahi hai aur mujh par ghalib honey ki koshish ki jari hai'' , wo ( Zohri ( kehtey hain : to jab logon ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey ye baat suni to log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key un namazon mein qirat karney sey ruk gaey jin mein aap buland aawaz sey qirat kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- ibne-Ukema Lesi ka naam Imaara hai unhen Amr bin Ukema bhi kaha jata hai, Zohri key deegar talaamiza ney bhi ye hadees riwayat ki hai lekin un logon ney isey un alfaz key sath zikr kya hai «قال الزهري فانتهى الناس an القراءة حين سمعوا ذلك من رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم» '' Zohri ney kaha ke log qirat sey ruk gaey jis waqt un logon ney isey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey suna '' padhi. 3- is bab mein ibne-Masood, Imran bin Husain aur Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- is hadees mein aisi koi chiz nahin hai jo un logon key liye rukawat ka sabab baney jinki raey Imam key peechey bhi qirat ki hai, isliye ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hi hain jinhoney ye hadees riwayat ki hai aur unhoney hi Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey ye hadees bhi riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya '' jisney koi namaz padhi aur is mein Sura Fatiha nahin padhi to wo naqis hai, naqis hai, na-tamam hai'' to un sey eik shakhs ney jisney un sey ye hadees akhaz ki thi puchha ke main kabhi Imam key peechey hota hun ( to kya karun?) to unhoney kaha : tum usey apney dil mein padh liya karo. abu-Usman Nahdi sey riwayat hai ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke mujhey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney ye hukm diya ke main aelan kar dun ke Sura Fatiha key baghair namaz nahin hoti , 5- aksar muhaddeseen ney is baat ko pasand kya hai ke jab Imam buland aawaz sey qirat karey to muqtadi qirat na kerey. aur kaha hai ke wo Imam key sakton ka « ittibaa » karta rahey, ''yani wo Imam key sakton key darmiyan padh liya karey '' , 6- Imam key peechey qirat key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, Sahaba o Tabe-een aur unkey baad key logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm Imam key peechey qirat key qaail hain, Malik bin Anas, Abdullah bin Mubarak Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain, Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain ke Imam key peechey qirat karta hun aur log bhi kartey hain siwaye koofiyon mein sey chand logon key, aur mera khayal hai ke jo na padhey uski bhi namaz durust hai, 7- aur ehle-ilm mein sey kuch logon ney is silsiley mein sakhti barti hai, un logon ka kehna hai ke Sura Fatiha ka chhodna jayez nahin agar-che wo Imam key peechey ho, ye log kehtey hain ke baghair Sura Fatiha key namaz kifaayat nahin karti , ye log is hadees ki taraf gaey hain jisey Ubada bin Samit ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey riwayat ki hai. aur khud Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key baad Imam key peechey qirat ki hai, unka amal Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key usi qol par raha hai ke Sura Fatiha key baghair namaz nahin, yehi Shafai aur Is-haq bin Raahviya waghera ka bhi qol hai, 8- rahey Ahmed bin Hanbal to wo kehtey hain ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key farman '' Sura Fatiha key baghair namaz nahin hoti '' ka matlab ye hai ke jab wo akeley namaz padh raha ho tab Sura Fatiha key baghair namaz nahin hogi. unhoney Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees sey ye istidlaal kya hai jis mein hai ke '' jisney koi rakat padhi aur is mein Sura Fatiha nahin padhi to uski namaz nahin hui siwaye iskey ke wo Imam key peechey ho padhi. ''. Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain ke ye Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key Sahaba main eik shakhs hain aur unhoney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key farman '' Sura Fatiha key baghair namaz nahin hoti '' ki tafseer ye ki hai ke ye hukm us shakhs key liye hai jo akeley padh raha ho. un sab key bawajud Ahmed bin Hanbal ney Imam key peechey Sura Fatiha padhney hi ko pasand kya hai aur kaha hai ke aadmi Sura Fatiha ko na chhodey bhale hi wo Imam key peechey ho."
313,"jisney koi rakat aisi padhi jis mein Sura Fatiha nahin padhi to usney namaz hi nahin padhi, siwaye uskey ke wo Imam key peechey ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
314,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab masjid mein dakhil hotey to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( par durood o salam bhejtey aur ye dua padhtey : «رب اغفر لي ذنوبي وافتح لي أبواب رحمتك» '' aey merey rab ! merey gunah bakhsh dey aur apni rehmat key darwazey merey liye khol dey '' aur jab nikaltey to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( par salaat ( durood ( o salam bhejtey aur ye kehtey : «رب اغفر لي ذنوبي وافتح لي أبواب فضلك» '' aey merey rab ! merey gunah bakhsh dey aur apney Fazal key darwazey merey liye khol dey ''.
315,"main Abdullah bin Hasan sey Makka mein mila to mainey un sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney mujh sey usey bayan kya aur kaha ke jab aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam dakhil hotey to ye kehtey «رب افتح لي باب رحمتك» '' aey merey rab ! apni rehmat key darwazey merey liye khol dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Fatima (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees (shawahid ki bana par) Hasan hai, warna iski sanad muttasil nahin hai, 2- Fatima bint Husain ney Fatima kubraa ko nahin paya hai, wo to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baad chand maah hi tak zinda rahey , 3- is bab mein abu-Humed , abu-Usaid aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
316,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi masjid aaye to bethney sey pehley do rakatein padhey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Qatada ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Muhammad bin Ajlan aur deegar kaee logon ney Aamir bin Abdullah bin Zuber sey bhi ye hadees riwayat ki hai jaisey Malik bin Anas ki riwayat hai, 3- Suhel bin abi Saleh padhi. ney ye hadees b-tareeq : « Aamir bin Abdullah bin Zuber an Amr bin Sulem Zarqi an Jabir bin Abdullah an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » sey riwayat ki hai, 4- ye hadees ghair mehfooz hai aur sahih abu-Qatada ki hadees hai, is baab mein Jabir , abu-Umama , Abu-Hurera , Abu-Zar aur Kaab bin Malik sey bhi ahadees aai hain, hamarey as-haab ka amal usi hadees par hai : unhoney mustahab qarar diya hai ke jab aadmi masjid mein dakhil ho to jab tak do rakatein na padh ley , na bethey illa ye ke uskey paas koi uzr ho, 5- Ali bin Madini kehtey hain : Suhel bin abi Saleh ki hadees mein ghalati hui hai."
317,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' siwaye qabristaan aur hamaam ( ghusl khaney ( key sari zamin masjid hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali Abdullah bin Amr , Abu-Hurera , Jabir , ibne-Abbas , Huzefa , Anas , abu-Umama aur Abu-Zar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, un logon ney kaha hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai puri zamin merey liye sajda gaah aur tahaarat o pakizgi ka zaria banai gaee hai, 2- abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees abdul-Azeez bin Muhammad sey do tareeq sey marvi hai, baaz logon ney abu-Saeed key wastey ka zikr kya hai aur baaz ney nahin kya hai, is hadees mein iztirab hai, Sufiyan Sory ney b-tareeq : « Amr bin Yahya an Abeeh an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » mursalan riwayat ki hai. aur Hammad bin Salma ney ye hadees b-tareeq : « Amr bin Yahya an Abeeh an abi Saeed an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » marfooan riwayat ki hai. aur Muhammad bin Is-haq ney bhi ye hadees b-tareeq : « Amr bin Yahya an Abeeh » aur unka kehna hai ke Yahya ki aksar ahadees aai Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey abu-Saeed hi key wastey sey marvi hain, lekin is mein unhoney abu-Saeed key wastey ka zikr nahin kya hai, goya Sory ki riwayat « Amr bin Yahya an Abeeh an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ziyada Sabit aur ziyada sahih hai."
318,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' jisney Allah ki raza key liye masjid banai , to Allah uskey liye usi jaisa ghar banaeyga '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar , umr , Ali , Abdullah bin Amr , Anas , ibne-Abbas , Aaisha , Umme-Habiba , Abu-Zar , Amr bin Abasa , Waasila Isqaa' , Abu-Hurera aur Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
319,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Allah key liye koi masjid banai , chhoti ho ya badi , Allah uskey liye jannat main eik ghar banaey ga""."
320,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney qabron ki ziyaarat karney wali aurton aur qabron par masaajid bananey waley aur chiragh jalaney waley logon par lanat farmaai hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma sey ahadees aai hain."
321,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein masjid mein sotey they aur hum nojawan they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm mein ki eik jamaat ney masjid mein soney ki ijazat di hai, ibne-Abbas kehtey hain : koi usey soney aur qeluley ki jagah na banaey padhi. aur baaz ehle-ilm ibne-Abbas key qol ki taraf gaey hain."
322,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney masjid mein ashaar padhney , kharid-farokht karney , aur Juma key din namaz ( Juma ( sey pehley halqa baandh kar bethney sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- Amr key baap Shuaib : Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas key betey hain padhi. , Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke mainey Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ko) aur un dono key ilawa unhoney kuch aur logon ka zikr kya hai) dekha ke ye log Amr bin Shuaib ki hadees sey istidlaal kartey they, Muhammad bin Ismail kehtey hain ke Shuaib bin Muhammad ney apney dada Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas Raziallahu anhuma sey suna hai, 3- jin logon ney Amr bin Shuaib ki hadees mein kalam karney walon ney unhen sirf isliye zaeef qarar diya hai ke wo apney dada ( Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma ( key sahifey ( saheefa saadiqa) sey riwayat kartey hain, goya un logon ka khayal hai ke ye ahadees unhoney apney dada sey nahin suni hain padhi. Ali bin Abdullah (ibne-Madeeni) kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed ( Qataan ( sey manqul hai ke unhoney kaha : Amr bin Shuaib ki hadees hamarey nazdik zaeef hai, 4- is bab mein Barida , Jabir aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 5- ehle-ilm mein sey kuch logon ney masjid mein kharid o farokht ko makrooh qarar diya hai, yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain padhi. , 6- aur Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm sey masjid mein kharid o farokht karney ki rukhsat marvi hai, 7- neez Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hadeeson mein masjid mein she'r padhney ki rukhsat marvi hai 4- ."
323,"bani Khadra key eik shakhs aur bani Amr bin Auf key eik shakhs key darmiyan behes ho gaee ke kon si masjid hai jiski buniyad taqwa par rakhi gaee padhi. to Khudri ney kaha : wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki masjid ( yani masjide-nabawi) hai, doosrey ney kaha : wo masjid quba hai, chunanche wo dono is silsiley mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye to aap ney farmaya : ''wo ye masjid hai, yani masjid nabawi aur is mein (yani masjid quba mein) bhi bahut khair o barkat hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Ali bin Abdullah bin Madini ney Yahya bin Saeed al-Qattaan sey (sanad mein mojud Raavi) Muhammad bin abi Yahya Aslami key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : un mein koi qabile-giraft baat nahin hai, aur unkey bhai Unais bin abi Yahya un sey ziyada Suqa (qabile-bharosa) hain."
324,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' masjid quba mein namaz padhney ka sawab eik Umra key barabar hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Usaid ki hadees Hasan, gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- hum Usaid bin Zuher ki koi aisi chiz nahin jantey jo sahih ho siwaye is hadees key."
325,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' meri is masjid ki eik namaz dusri masaajid ki hazar namazon sey ziyada behtar hai, siwaye masjide-Haram key ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- kaee sanadon sey marvi hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Ali , Memuna , abu-Saeed , Juber bin Mut-im , ibne-Umar , Abdullah bin Zuber aur Abu-Zar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
326,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' teen masaajid key siwa kisi aur jagah key liye safar na kya jaey, 1- masjide-Haram key liye , 2- meri is masjid (masjid nabawi) key liye, 3- masjide-Aqsa key liye''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
327,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab namaz ki takbir ( iqaamat ( keh di jaey to ( namaz mein sey) uski taraf daud kar mat aao , balke chaltey huye us haal mein aao ke tum par sakeenat taari ho, to jo paao usey padho aur jo chhoot jaey, usey puri karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein abu-Qatada , Ubai-bin Kaab , abu-Saeed , Zaid bin Sabit , Jabir aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 2- ehle-ilm ka masjid ki taraf chal kar janey mein ikhtilaf hai : un mein sey baaz ki raey hai ke jab takbir tahreema key faut honey ka dar ho, wo dodey yahan tak ke baaz logon key barey mein mazkur hai ke wo namaz key liye qadrey daud kar jatey they aur baaz logon ney daud kar janey ko makrooh qarar diya hai aur aahisatagi o waqar sey janey ko pasand kya hai. yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain, un dono ka kehna hai ke amal Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees par hai. aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke agar takbir tahreema key chhoot janey ka dar ho to daud kar janey mein koi muzaaeqa nahin."
328,Abu-Hurera key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi mafhoom key sath marvi hai jaisey abu-Salma ki hadees hai jisey unhoney Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki hai. isi tarah kaha hai abdur-Razzaaq ney wo riwayat kartey hain ke Saeed bin al-Musayab sey aur Saeed bin Musaiyab ney b-wasta Abu-Hurera sey aur Abu-Hurera ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai aur ye Yazeed bin Zurey ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai padhi. .
329,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah marvi hai.
330,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aadmi barabar namaz hi mein rehta hai jab tak wo uska intizar karta hai aur farishtey uskey liye barabar dua kartey rehtey hain jab tak wo masjid mein rehta hai, kehtey hain « اللهم اغفر له  '' Allah ! usey bakhsh dey '' « اللهم ارحمه » '' aey Allah ! is par reham farma '' jab tak wo « hadas » nahin karta '' , to Hazare-maut key eik shakhs ney puchha : « hadas » kya hai Abu-Hurera ? to Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aahista sey ya zor sey huwa khaarij karna padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , abu-Saeed , Anas , Abdullah bin Masood aur Sehal bin Saad (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
331,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam « خمرہ » '' chhoti chataai '' par namaz padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Umme-Habiba , ibne-Umar , Umme Sulem , Aaisha , Memuna , Umme kulsoom bint abi Salma bin Abdul-Asad ( Umme kulsoom bint abi Salma ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey nahin suna hai) aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka yehi khayal hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey « خمرہ » par namaz Sabit hai, 4- « خمرہ » chhoti chataai ko kehtey hain."
332,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney chataai par namaz padhi padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas aur Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai, albatta ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney zamin par namaz padhney ko istehbab ke taur par pasand kya hai."
333,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hum sey ghul mil jaya kartey they. yahan tak ke aap merey chhotey bhai sey kehtey : ابوعمیر ! « ما amal النغير » '' bulbul ka kya huwa? '' hamari chataai padhi. par chhidkaaw kya gaya phir aap ney is par namaz padhi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai. wo chadar aur qalin par namaz padhney mein koi qabaahat nahin samajhtey yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain."
334,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam baghaat mein namaz padhna pasand farmatey they. abu-Daawood kehtey hain : Hetaan sey murad « بساتین » '' baghaat '' hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Muaz ki hadees gharib hai, usey hum Hasan bin abi Jaafar hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Hasan bin abi Jaafar ko Yahya bin Saeed waghera ney zaeef qarar diya hai."
335,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum sey koi apney aagey kajawey ki pichhli lakdi ki maanind koi chiz rakh ley to namaz padhey aur uski parwah na karey ke uskey aagey sey kon guzra hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Sehal bin abi Hasma , ibne-Umar , Sabra bin Maabad Juhni, abu-Juhaifa aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
336,"Zaid bin Khalid Juhni ney unhen Abu Juhaim (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bheja taake wo un sey ye poochen ke unhoney namazi ke aage se guzarney waley key barey mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kya suna hai? to Abu Juhaim (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : agar namazi ke aagey sey guzarney wala jaan ley ke is par kya (gunah) hai to uskey liye namazi ke aagey sey guzarney sey chaalis … tak khada rehna behtar hoga. abu-Nazar Salim kehtey hain : mujhey nahin malum ke unhoney chaalis din kaha , ya chaalis mahiney kaha ya chaalis saal. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu Juhaim (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Umar aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey kisi ka sau saal khadey rehna is baat sey behtar hai ke wo apney bhai key samney sey guzrey aur wo namaz padh raha ho.''  4- ehle-ilm key nazdik amal isi par hai, un logon ney namazi key aagey sey guzarney ko makrooh jana hai, lekin un ki ye raey nahin ke aadmi ki namaz ko batil kar dega."
337,"Main eik gadhi par (apney bhai) Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey sawar tha, hum aaye aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Meena mein Sahaba ko namaz padha rahey they, hum gadhi sey utrey aur saf mein mil gaey. aur wo (gadhi) un logon key samney phirney lagi, to usney un ki namaz batil nahin ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Fazal bin Abbas aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba aur un ke baad Tabe-een mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke namaz ko koi chiz batil nahin karti, Sufiyan Sory aur Shafai bhi yehi kehtey hain."
338,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab aadmi namaz padhey aur uskey samney kajawey ki aakhiri (lakdi ya kaha : kajawey ki bech ki lakdi ki tarah) koi chiz na ho to : kaley kuttey , aurat aur gadhey key guzarney sey uski namaz batil ho jaeygi.'' padhi. mainey Abu-Zar sey kaha : lal , aur safed ke muqabley mein kalay ki kya khasusiyaat hai? unhoney kaha : merey bhatijey ! tum ney mujh sey aisey hi puchha hai jaisey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha tha to aap ney farmaya : ''kaalaa kutta shetan hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu Saeed Khudri , Hukam bin Amr bin Ghifaarii , Abu-Hurera aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm isi taraf gaey hain, wo kehtey hain ke gadhaa , aurat aur kaalaa kutta namaz ko batil kar deta hai. Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : mujhey is mein koi shak nahin ke kaalaa kutta namaz batil kar deta hai lekin gadhey aur aurat key silsiley mein mujhey kuchh tazabzub hai, Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : kalay kuttey key siwa koi aur chiz namaz batil nahin karti."
339,"unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko Ummul-momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) key ghar mein is haal mein namaz padhtey dekha , ke aap eik kapdey mein liptay huye they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- umr bin abi Salma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Jabir , Salma bin Al Akwaa, Anas , Amr bin abi Usaid , Ubada bin Samit , abu Saeed Khudri , Kaisaan , ibne-Abbas , Aaisha , Umme-Haani , Ammar bin Yasir , Talaq bin Ali , aur Ubada bin Samit Ansari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. Sahaba kiram aur unke baad Tabe-een waghaira sey aksar ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai, wo kehtey hain ke eik kapdey mein namaz padhney mein koi harj nahin aur baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha hai ke aadmi do kapdon mein namaz padhey."
340,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Madiney aaye to sola ya satarah maah tak aap ney Baitul-Maqdis ki taraf rukh kar ke namaz padhi aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Kaba ki taraf rukh karna pasand farmatey they to Allah Taala ney (قد نرى تقلب وجهك في السماء فلنولينك قبلة ترضاها فول وجهك شطر المسجد الحرام). ''ham aap ke chehrey ko baar-baar aasman ki taraf uthtey huye dekh rahey hain, ab hum aap ko us qibley ki janib mutawajjeh karengey jis sey aap khush ho jaeyn , ab aap apna rukh Masjide-Haram ki taraf pher lijiye.'' nazil farmaee, to aap ney apna chehra Kaba ki taraf pher liya aur aap yehi chahtey bhi they, eik shakhs ney aap key sath Asr padhi , phir wo ansaar key kuchh logon key paas sey guzra aur wo log Asr mein Baitul-Maqdis ki taraf chehra kiye rukoo ki haalat mein they, usne kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke sath is haal mein namaz padhi hai ke aap apna rukh Kaba ki taraf kiye huye they. to wo log bhi rukoo ki haalat hi mein (Khane Kaba ki taraf) phir gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Bara ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , ibne-Abbas , Imaara bin Aus , Amr bin Auf Muzni aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
341,wo log namaz Fajr mein rukoo mein they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai.
342,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mashriq ( purab (aur maghrib ( pashchim ( key darmiyan jo hai sab qibla hai'' padhi. .
343,"hum sey Muhammad bin abi Maashar ney bhi usi key misl bayan kya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees un sey aur bhi kaee sanadon sey marvi hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ney abu-Maashar key hifz key talluq sey kalam kya hai. unka naam najeeh hai, wo bani Hashim key Mola hain, 3- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : main un sey koi riwayat nahin karta halanke logon ney un sey riwayat ki hai neez Bukhari kehtey hain ke Abdullah bin Jaafar Makhrami ki hadees jisey unhoney basanad « Usman bin Muhammad Akhnasi an Saeed al-Maqbari an Abi Hurera» riwayat ki hai, abu-Ma'shar ki hadees sey ziyada qawi aur ziyada sahih hai) ye hadees aagey aa rahi hai jo usi maana ki hai) ."
344,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' mashriq ( purab (aur maghrib ( pashchim ( key darmiyan jo hai wo sab qibla hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- kaee Sahaba sey marvi hai ke mashriq o maghrib key darmiyan jo hai sab qibla hai. un mein umr bin Khattab , Ali bin abi Talib , aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) bhi shamil hain, ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : jab aap maghrib ko daain taraf aur mashriq ko baain taraf rakh kar qibla rukh khadey hongey to un dono simton key darmiyan jo hoga wo qibla hoga, ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain : mashriq o maghrib key darmiyan jo hai sab qibla hai, ye ehle-mashriq padhi. key liye hai. aur Abdullah bin Mubarak ney ehal maro padhi. key liye baain taraf jhukney ko pasand kya hai."
345,"hum eik taareek raat mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath safar mein they. to hum nahin jaan sakey ke qibla kis taraf hai, hum mein sey har shakhs ney usi taraf rukh kar key namaz padh li jis taraf pehley sey uska rukh tha. jab hamney subh ki aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uska zikr kya chunanche us waqt aayate-karima « ‏فأينما تولوا فثم وجه الله‏ » '' tum jis taraf rukh kar lo Allah ka munh usi taraf hai'' nazil hui . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad kuch ziyada achi nahin hai. hum isey sirf Ash-as bin samaan hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Ash-as bin Saeed abu-Rabee samaan hadees key mamley mein zaeef maaney jatey hain, 2- aksar ehle-ilm isi ki taraf gaey hain ke jab koi badli mein ghair qibley ki taraf namaz padh ley phir namaz padh leney key baad pata chaley usney ghair qibley ki taraf rukh kar key namaz padhi hai to uski namaz durust hai. Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain."
346,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney saat maqamat mein namaz padhney sey mana farmaya hai : kudra karkat dalney ki jagah mein , mazbah mein , qabristaan mein , aam raaston par , hamaam ( ghusl khaney ( mein oont baandhney ki jagah mein aur Baitullah ki chhat par ."
347,"is mafhoom ki hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees ki sanad koi ziyada qawi nahin hai, Zaid bin Jubaira ke silsiley mein un ke hifz ke talluq sey kalam kiya gaya hai. 2- Zaid bin Juber Koofi un sey ziyada qawi aur un sey pehley ke hain unhoney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey suna hai. 3- is bab mein Abu Mursad Kinaaz bin Husen, Jabir aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadeen aai hain. 4- Les bin Saad ney ye hadees ba-tareeq : (Abdullah bin umr an Nafey an ibne-Umar an umr an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi Wasallam) isi tarah riwayat ki hai. Dawud ki hadees jisey unhoney b-tareeq : (an Nafey an ibne-Umar an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi Wasallam) sey riwayat ki hai. Les bin Saad ki hadees sey ziyada sawaab wali aur ziyada sahih hai. Abdullah bin umr Umri ko baaz ehale-hadees ney unke hifz ke talluq sey zaeef maana hai, unhi mein sey Yahya bin Saeed Al Qattan bhi hain."
348,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bakriyon key baadey mein namaz padho padhi. aur oont baandhney ki jagah mein na padho.''
349,"Isi ke jaisi ya isi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, hamarey as-haab (saathiyon) ke nazdik amal usi par hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai, 2- abu-Husen ki hadees jisey unhoney b-tareeq : (abi Saleh an Abi Hurera an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai gharib hai. 3- usey Israel ney b-tareeq : (Abi Husen an abi Saleh an Abi Hurera) moqufan riwayat kiya hai, aur unhoney usey marfoo nahin kiya hai. 4- is bab mein Jabir bin Samura , Bara , Sabra bin Maabad Juhni, Abdullah bin Mughaffal , ibne-Umar aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
350,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bakriyon key baadey mein namaz padhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
351,"Mujhey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik zarurat sey bheja to main zarurat puri kar ke aaya to (dekha ke) aap apni sawari par mashriq (purab) ki taraf rukh kar ke namaz padh rahey they, aur sajda rukoo se ziyada past (jhuka) tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, ye hadees deegar aur sanadon sey bhi Jabir sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas , ibne-Umar , abu-Saeed , Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain, 3- aur usi par beshtar ehle-ilm ke nazdik amal hai, hum unke darmiyan koi ikhtilaf nahin jantey, ye log aadmi ke apni sawari par nafl namaz padhney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey, chahey uska rukh qibley ki taraf ho ya kisi aur taraf ho."
352,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney oont ya apni sawari ki taraf munh kar ke namaz padhi , isi ke saath apni sawari par namaz padhtey rehtey chahey wo jis taraf mutawajjeh hoti padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- yehi baaz ehle-ilm ka qol hai ke oont ko sutarah (aad) bana kar uski taraf munh kar key namaz padhney mein koi harj nahin."
353,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Sham ka khana hazir ho, aur namaz khadi kar di jaey padhi. to pehley kha lo.''.Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , ibne-Umar , Salma bin Akwaa , aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. unhi mein sey Abu-Bakar , umr aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) bhi hain, aur yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain ke pehley khana khaye agar-che jamaat chhoot jaey 4- is hadees ke barey mein kehtey hain ke wo pehley khana khayega jab usey khana kharab honey ka andesha ho, lekin jiski taraf Sahaba kiram waghera mein sey baaz ehle-ilm gaey hain, wo ittiba key ziyada laaiq hai, un logon ka maqsad ye hai ke aadmi aisi haalat mein namaz mein na khada ho ke uska dil kisi chiz ke sabab mashghool ho, aur ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai ke hum namaz key liye khadey nahin hotey jab tak hamara dil kisi aur chiz mein laga hota hai."
354,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Sham ka khana (tumharey samney) rakh diya jaey aur namaz khadi ho jaey to pehley khana khaoo.''  ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma Sham ka khana kha rahey they aur Imam ki qirat sun rahey they.
355,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi unghey aur wo namaz padh raha ho to so jaey yahan tak ke us sey neend chali jaey, isliye ke tum mein sey koi jab namaz padhey aur ungh raha ho to shayad wo istighfar karna chahta ho lekin apney aap ko gaaliyaan dey bethey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
356,"Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) hamari namaz padhney ki jagah mein aatey aur hadees bayan kartey they to eik din namaz ka waqt huwa to hamne un sey kaha ke aap aagey badhey (aur namaz padhaaen). unhoney kaha : tumhin mein sey koi aagey badh kar namaz padhaaey yahan tak ke main tumhen bataaun ke main kyon nahin aagey badhta , mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''jo kisi qom ki ziyaarat ko jaey to un ki imaamat na karey balke un ki imaamat un hi mein sey kisi aadmi ko karni chahiye.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke sahibe khana (ghar wala) ziyaarat karney waley (aane wale) sey ziyada imaamat ka haqdaar hai, baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke jab usey ijazat dey di jaey to uskey namaz padhaaney mein koi harj nahin hai, Is-haq bin Raahviya ney Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ke mutabiq kaha hai aur unhoney is masle mein sakhti barti hai ke sahibe khana (ghar walon) ko koi aur namaz na padhaaey agar-che sahibe khana usey ijazat dedey, isi ke saath wo kehtey hain : isi tarah ka hukm masjid key barey mein bhi hai ke wo jab un ki ziyaarat key liye aaya ho unhi mein sey kisi aadmi ko un ki namaz padhaani chahiye."
357,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi aadmi key liye jayez nahin ke wo kisi key ghar key andar jhank kar dekhey jab tak ke ghar mein dakhil honey ki ijazat na ley ley. agar usney (jhank kar) dekha to goya wo andar dakhil ho gaya. aur koi logon ki imaamat is tarah na karey ke in ko chhod kar dua ko sirf apney liye khas karey. agar usney aisa kiya to usney un sey khayanat ki. aur na koi namaz key liye khada ho aur haal ye ho ke wo pakhana aur peshab ko rokey huye ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye hadees Muawiya bin Saleh sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai, Muawiya ney is ko b-tareeq : (Safar bin Nusair an Yazeed bin Shureh  an abi Umama an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam)  riwayat ki hai, isi ke saath ye hadees Yazeed bin Shureh hi key wastey sey b-tareeq : (Abi Hurera an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki gaee hai. Yazeed bin Shureh ki hadees b-tareeq : Abi Hayyi Muazzin an Soban) sanad ke aetbar sey sab sey umda aur mashhoor hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Abu-Umama Raziallahu anhuma sey hadeesen aai hain."
358,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney teen logon par lanat farmaee hai : eik wo shakhs jo logon ki imaamat karey aur log usey napasand kartey hon. dusri wo aurat jo raat guzaarey aur uska shohar us sey naraz ho. teesra wo jo (حي على الفلاح) suney aur uska jawab na dey (yani jamaat mein hazir na ho). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees sahih nahin hai kyonkey haqiqat mein ye hadees Hasan ( Basraa ( sey baghair kisi wastey ke Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 2- Muhammad bin Qasim key silsiley mein Ahmed bin Hanbal ney kalam kya hai, unhoney unhen zaeef qarar diya hai. aur ye ke wo Hafiz nahin hain. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Talha , Abdullah bin Amr aur abu-Umama (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ke yahan ye makrooh hai ke aadmi logon ki imaamat karey aur wo usey napasand kartey hon aur jab Imam zalim (qasoorwar) na ho to gunah usi par hoga jo napasand karey. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka is silsiley mein ye kehna hai ke jab eik ya do ya teen log napasand karen to uskey unhen namaz padhaaney mein koi harj nahin, siwaaye iske ke logon ki aksariyat usey napasand karti ho."
359,"Kaha jata tha ke qiyamat key roz sab sey sakht azab do tarah key logon ko hoga : eik us aurat ko jo apney shohar ki nafarmani karey, doosrey us Imam ko jisey log napasand kartey hon. Mansoor kehtey hain ke hamney Imam key mamley mein puchha to hamein bataya gaya ke us sey murad zalim Aaimma hain, lekin jo Imam sunnat qaaim karey to gunah is par hoga jo usey napasand karey."
360,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( ney farmaya : ''teen logon ki namaz un ke kanon sey ooper nahin jati : eik bhagaude ghulam ki jab tak ke wo (apney Malik key paas) lot na aaye, doosrey aurat ki jo raat guzaarey aur uska shohar us sey naraz ho, teesrey us Imam ki jisey log napasand kartey hon.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
361,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ghodey sey gir padey, aap ko kharaash aa gaee padhi. to aap ney hamein beth kar namaz padhaai, hum ne bhi aap ke sath beth kar namaz padhi. phir aap ney hamari taraf palat kar farmaya : ''Imam hota hi isliye hai ya Imam banaya hi isliye gaya hai taake uski iqtida (pairvi) ki jaey, jab wo « الله أكبر » kahey to tum bhi « الله أكبر » kaho , aur jab wo rukoo karey , to tum bhi rukoo karo, aur jab wo sar uthaey to tum bhi sar uthao , aur jab wo « samiallahu-liman hamida » kahey to tum « ربنا لك الحمد‏ » kaho, aur jab wo sajda karey to tum bhi sajda karo aur jab wo beth kar namaz padhey to tum sab bhi beth kar namaz padho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Abu-Hurera , Jabir , ibne-Umar aur Muawiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain, 3- baaz Sahaba kiram jin mein mein Jabir bin Abdullah , Usaid bin Huzer aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) waghera hain isi hadees ki taraf gaey hain aur yehi qol Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi hai, 4- baaz ehle-ilm ka kehna hai ke jab Imam beth kar padhey to muqtadi khadey ho kar hi padhen , agar unhoney beth kar padhi to ye namaz unhen kafi na hogi , ye Sufiyan Sory , Malik bin Anas , ibne-Mubarak aur Shafai ka qol hai."
362,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni us bimari mein jis mein aap ki wafat hui abu-Bakar key peechhey beth kar namaz padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. aur Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Imam beth kar namaz padhey to tum bhi beth kar namaz padho.''  aur un sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke ''Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni bimari mein nikley aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko namaz padha rahey they to aap ney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key pehlu mein namaz padhi , log abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they. aur unhi sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey beth kar namaz padhi. aur Anas bin Malik sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey beth kar namaz padhi."
363,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni bimari mein abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey beth kar namaz padhi aur aap eik kapdey mein liptey huye they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi tarah usey Yahya bin Ayub ney bhi Humed sey, aur Humed ney Sabit sey aur Sabit ney Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kiya hai. 3- isi ke saath isey aur bhi kaee logon ney Humed sey aur Humed ney Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kiya hai, aur un logon ney is mein Sabit ke wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai, lekin jisney Sabit key wastey ka zikr kiya hai, wo ziyada sahih hai."
364,"Hamein Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ney namaz padhaai , do rakat key baad (bethney ke bajaey) wo khadey ho gaey, to logon ney unhen (Subhan-Allah) keh kar yad dilaaya ke wo beth jaeyn to unhoney (Subhan-Allah) keh kar unhen ishara kiya ke wo log khadey ho jaeyn, phir jab unhoney apni baqiya namaz padh li to salam pheraa phir bethey bethey sahoo ke do sajdey kiye. phir logon se hadees bayan ki ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon ke sath aisa hi kiya tha jaisey unhoney (Mughira ney) kiya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees un sey kaee aur bhi sanadon sey marvi  (riwayat hui) hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm ney ibne-Abi Leila ke silsiley mein un ke hifz ke talluq sey kalam kiya hai. Ahmed kehtey hain : ibne-Abi Leila ki hadees laaiqe daleel  hain. 3۔ Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : ibne-Abi Leila Sadooq (sachchey) hain lekin main un sey riwayat nahin karta isliye ke ye nahin malum ke un ki hadisein kon si sahih hain aur kon si zaeef hain, aur jo bhi aisa ho main us sey riwayat nahin karta.  4- ye hadees Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey aur bhi sanadon sey marvi  (riwayat hui) hai. 5- isey Sufiyan ney b-tareeq : (Jabir an Mughira bin Shubail an Qais bin abi Hazim an Mughira bin Sho'ba) riwayat kiya hai. aur Jabir Jua'fi ko baaz ehle-ilm ney zaeef qarar diya hai, Yahya bin Saeed aur Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi waghera ney un sey hadisein nahin li hain, 6- is bab mein Aqba bin Aamir , Saad aur Abdullah bin Buhena (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 7- isi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai ke aadmi jab do rakatein padh kar khada ho jaey to apni namaz jari rakhey aur (aakheer mein) do sajdey kar ley. 8- un mein sey baaz ka khayal hai ke sajdey salam pherney sey pehley karey aur baaz ka khayal hai ke salam pherney key baad karey 9-  jis ka khayal hai ke salam pher ney sey pehley karey uski hadees ziyada sahih hai isliye ke usey Zohri aur Yahya bin Saeed Ansari ney Abdur-Rehman bin Aaraj sey aur Abdur-Rehman ney Abdullah ibn Buhena (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kiya hai."
365,"Hamein Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ney namaz padhaai , jab do rakatein padh chukey to (tashahud mein) baghair bethey khadey ho gaey. to jo log un ke peechhey they unhoney subhan Allah kaha , to unhoney unhen ishara kiya ke tum bhi khadey ho jaao phir jab wo apni namaz sey farigh huye to unhoney salam pheraa aur sahoo ke do sajdey kiye aur salam pheraa , aur kaha : aisey hi Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kiya tha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ke wastey sey aur bhi sanadon sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
366,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab pehli dono rakaaton mein bethtey to aisa lagta goya aap garm pathar par bethey hain, Shoba ( Raavi ( kehtey hain : phir Saad ney apney dono honton ko kisi chiz ke sath harkat di padhi. to mainey kaha : yahan tak ke aap khadey ho jatey? to unhoney kaha : yahan tak ke aap khadey ho jatey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai.2 magar abu-Ubaida ne apney baap sey sunaa nahin hai. 3- ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai, wo usi ko pasand kartey hain ke aadmi pehli dono rakaaton mein qaada ko lamba na karey aur tashahud sey ziyada kuchh na padhey, un logon ka kehna hai ke agar usney tashahud sey ziyada koi chiz padhi to is par sahoo key do sajdey lazim ho jaeyngey, Shaabi waghera sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
367,"Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke paas sey guzra aur aap namaz padh rahey they, mainey salam kiya to aap ney mujhey isharay sey jawab diya, Raavi ( ibne-Umar ( kehtey hain ke mera yehi khayal hai ke Suheb ney kaha : aap ney apni ungli ke isharey sey jawab diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Suheb ki hadees Hasan hai.  2- is bab mein Bilal , Abu-Hurera , Anas , Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
368,"mainey Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha ke Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Sahaba ko jab wo salam kartey aur aap namaz mein hotey to kaisey jawab detey they? to Bilal ney kaha : aap apney haath key ishara sey jawab detey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur Suheb ki hadees Hasan hai, hum isey sirf Les hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain unhoney Buker sey riwayat ki hai aur ye Zaid ibne Aslam sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai wo ibne-Umar sey riwayat kartey hain ke mainey Bilal sey puchha : Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kis tarah jawab detey they jab log masjid bani Amr bin Auf mein aap ko salam kartey they? to unhoney jawab diya ke aap isharay sey jawab detey they. merey nazdik dono hadisein sahih hain, isliye ke Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ka qissa Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) key qissey ke ilawa hai, agar-che ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney un dono sey riwayat ki hai, to is baat ka ehtimaal (gumaan) hai ke unhoney dono sey suna ho."
369,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''namaz mein mardon key liye ''Subhan-Allah'' keh kar Imam ko uskey sahoo par mutanabbeh (aagah) karna aur aurton key liye dastak dena hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Sehal bin Saad , Jabir , abu-Saeed , ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke jab main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey andar aaney ki ijazat maangta aur aap namaz padh rahey hotey to aap Subhan-Allah kehtey. 4- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain."
370,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''namaz mein jamaai aana shetan ki taraf sey hai, jab tum mein sey kisi ko jamaai aaye to jahan tak ho sakey usey rokey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri aur Adi bin Sabit ke daada ( Ubaid bin Aazib ( sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm mein sey kuchh logon ney namaz mein jamaai leney ko makrooh kaha hai, Ibrahim kehtey hain ke main jamaai ko khankhar sey lota deta hun."
371,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aadmi ki namaz ke barey mein puchha jisey wo beth kar padh raha ho? to aap ney farmaya : ''jo khadey ho kar namaz padhey wo beth kar padhney waley key bilmuqaabil afzal hai, kyonkey usey khadey ho kar padhney waley sey aadha sawab milega, aur jo let kar padhey usey beth kar padhney waley sey aadha milega.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Imran bin Husain ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr , Anas , Saaib aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
372,"Isi sanad sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, magar is mein yun hai : Imran bin Husain kehtey hain ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mareez ki namaz ke barey mein sawal kiya to aap ney farmaya : ''khadey ho kar padho, agar uski taqat na ho to beth kar padho aur agar uski bhi taqat na ho to let kar pehlu key bal padho.''"
373,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko kabhi beth kar nafl namaz padhtey nahin dekha , yahan tak ke jab wafat main eik saal reh gaya to aap beth kar nafli namaz padhney lagey. aur sura padhtey to is tarah thehar thehar kar padhtey ke wo lambi sey lambi ho jati. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Hafsa (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Umme-Salma aur Anas bin Malik Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hai. 3- Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap raat ko beth kar namaz padhtey aur jab tees ya chaalis aayaton key ba-qadr qirat baqi reh jati to aap khadey ho jatey aur qirat kartey phir rukoo mein jatey۔ phir dusri rakat mein bhi isi tarah kartey. aur aap sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap beth kar namaz padhtey. aur jab khadey ho kar qirat kartey to rukoo aur sajda bhi khadey ho kar kartey aur jab beth kar qirat kartey to rukoo aur sajda bhi beth hi kar kartey. 4- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke dono hadisein sahih aur mamool bhi hain."
374,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam beth kar namaz padhtey to qirat bhi beth hi kar kartey , phir jab tees ya chaalis aayaton key b-qadr qirat baqi reh jati to aap khadey ho jatey aur unhen khadey ho kar padhtey phir rukoo aur sajda kartey phir dusri rakat mein bhi isi tarah kartey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
375,mainey ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki nafl namaz key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : aap raat tak khadey ho kar namaz padhtey aur der tak beth kar padhtey jab aap khadey ho kar qirat kartey to rukoo aur sajda bhi khadey khadey kartey aur jab beth kar qirat kartey to rukoo aur sajda bhi beth kar hi kartey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
376,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' qism hai Allah ki ! jab namaz mein hota hun aur us waqt bachey ka rona sunta hun to us dar sey namaz ko halki kar deta hun ke uski maa kahin fitney mein na mubtala ho jaey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Qatada abu-Saeed aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
377,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' baligh aurat ki namaz baghair odhni key qubul nahin ki jati '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke jab aurat baligh ho jaey aur namaz padhey aur uskey baal ka kuch hissey khula ho to uski namaz jayez nahin, yehi Shafai ka bhi qol hai, wo kehtey hain ke aurat is haal mein namaz padhey ke uskey jism ka kuch hissey khula ho jayez nahin, neez Shafai ye bhi kehtey hain ke kaha gaya hai : agar uskey dono paaon ki pusht khuli ho to namaz durust hai."
378,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney namaz mein sadal kerney (chadar ko dono kandhon par daalkar latakta chhod deney) sey mana farmaya hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hum Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ko ata ki riwayat sey jisey unhoney Abu-Hurera sey marfooan riwayat ki hai Asl bin Sufiyan hi key tareeq sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- sadal key silsiley mein ehle-ilm key darmiyan ikhtilaf hai : baaz log kehtey hain ke namaz mein sadal karna makrooh hai, unka kehna hai ke is tarah Yahud kartey hain aur baaz kehtey hain ke namaz mein sadal us waqt makrooh hoga jab jism par eik hi kapda ho, rahi ye baat ke jab koi kartey key ooper sadal karey to is mein koi muzaaeqa nahin padhi. yehi Ahmed ka qol hai lekin ibne-Mubarak ney namaz mein sadal ko) bilkul) makrooh qarar diya hai."
379,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi namaz key liye khada ho to apney samney sey kankariyaan na hataaey padhi. kyonkey Allah ki rehmat uska samna kar rahi hoti hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Zar ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Muaiqeeb, Ali bin abi Talib, Huzefa , Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi hai ke aap ney namaz mein kankari hataney ko napasand kya hai aur farmaya hai ke agar hatana zaruri ho to eik baar hata dey, goya aap sey eik baar ki rukhsat marvi hai, 4- aur usi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai."
380,mainey namaz mein kankari hataney key silsiley mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha to aap ney farmaya : '' agar hataana zaruri hi ho to eik baar hata lo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
381,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamarey ( ghar key (eik ladkey ko dekha jisey Aflah kaha jata tha ke jab wo sajda karta to phunk maarta hai, to aap ney farmaya : '' Aflah ! apney chehrey ko gird aaluda kar''. Ahmed bin Munee kehtey hain ke Ibaad bin Awam ney namaz mein phunk maarney ko makrooh qarar diya hai aur kaha hai ke agar kisi ney phunk maar hi di to uski namaz batil na hogi . Ahmed bin Munee kehtey hain ke usi ko hum bhi ikhtiyar kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees ko baaz deegar logon ney abu-Hamza key wastey sey riwayat ki hai. aur « غلاما لنا يقال له أفلح » key bajaey « مولى لنا يقال له Ribah » ( hamarey Mola ko jisey Ribah kaha jata tha ( kaha hai."
382,"Memun abi Hamza sey usi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai aur is mein «غلام لنا يقال له رباح» hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees ki sanad kuch ziyada qawi nahin, Memun abu-Hamza ko baaz ehle-ilm ney zaeef qarar diya hai, 2- aur namaz mein phunk maarney key silsiley mein ehle-ilm key darmiyan ikhtilaf hai, baaz logon ka kehna hai ke agar koi shakhs namaz mein phunk maarey to wo namaz dobara padhey, yehi qol Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka hai. aur baaz ney kaha hai ke namaz mein phunk maarna makrooh hai, aur agar kisi ney apni namaz mein phunk maar hi di to uski namaz faasid na hogi, yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya waghera ka qol hai."
383,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kokh par haath rakh kar namaz padhney sey mana farmaya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadees aai hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ney namaz mein kokh par haath rakhney ko makrooh qarar diya hai, aur baaz ney aadmi key kokh par haath rakh kar chalney ko makrooh kaha hai, aur ikhtisaar ye hai ke aadmi namaz mein apna haath apni kokh par rakhey , ya apney dono haath apni kokhon par rakhey. aur riwayat ki jati hai ke shetan jab chalta hai to kokh par haath rakh kar chalta hai."
384,"wo Hasan bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma key paas sey guzrey , wo namaz padh rahey they aur apni guddi par jooda baandh rakha tha, abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) ney isey khol diya, Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ney un ki taraf ghussey sey dekha to unhoney kaha : apni namaz par tawajjoh do aur ghussa na karo kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey suna hai ke '' ye shetan ka hissa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Umme-Salma aur Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- isi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai. un logon ney is baat ko makrooh kaha ke namaz padhey aur wo apney baalon ka joda baandhey ho."
385,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' namaz do do rakat hai aur har do rakat key baad tashahud hai, namaz khushu o khuzoo, mohtaji aur giryaa wazari ka izhar hai, aur tum apney dono haath. uthaao yani tum apney dono haath apney rab key samney uthaao us haal mein ke hatheliyan tumharey munh ki taraf hun aur keh : aey rab ! aey rab ! aur jisney aisa nahin kya wo aisa aisa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Mubarak key ilawa aur logon ney is hadees mein « من لم يفعل ذلك فهي خداج » '' jisney aisa nahin kya uski namaz naqis hai'' kaha hai, 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko ye kehtey huye suna ke Shoba ney ye hadees abde-rabba bin Saeed sey riwayat ki hai aur un sey kaee maqamat par ghaltiyaan hui hain : eik to ye ke unhoney Anas bin abi Anas sey riwayat ki halanke wo Imran bin abi Anas hain, doosrey ye ke unhoney « an Abdullah bin Haris » kaha hai halanke wo « Abdulllah bin Nafey bin al-umiya an Rabia bin al-Haaris » hai, teesrey ye ke Shoba ney « an Abdullah bin al-Haaris an Muttalib an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » kaha hai halanke sahih « an Rabia bin al-Haaris bin abdul-Muttalib an al-Fazal bin Abbas an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » hai. Muhammad bin Ismail ( Bukhari ( kehtey hain : Les bin Saad ki hadees sahih hai yani Shoba ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai) warna aslan to zaeef hi hai)."
386,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi shakhs achi tarah sey wuzu karey aur phir masjid key iraday sey nikley to wo « tashbik » na karey ( yani eik haath ki ungliyon ko doosrey haath ki ungliyon mein pewast na karey ( kyonkey wo namaz mein hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Kaab bin Ajra ki hadees ko ibn Ajlan sey kaee logon ney Les wali hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai, 2- aur shareek ney b-tareeq : « Muhammad bin Ajlan an Abeeh an abi Hurera an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » isi hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai aur shareek ki riwayat ghair mehfooz hai."
387,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya : kon si namaz afzal hai? to aap ney farmaya : '' jis mein qiyam lamba ho '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai aur ye deegar sanadon sey bhi Jabir bin Abdullah sey marvi hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Habshi aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
388,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key azad karda ghulam Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey mulaqat ki aur un sey kaha ke aap mujhey koi aisa amal bataeyn jis sey Allah Taala mujhey nafa pahunchaey aur mujhey jannat mein dakhil karey , to wo kafi der tak khamosh rahey phir wo meri taraf mutawajjeh huye aur unhoney kaha ke tum kasrat sey sajdey kya karo padhi. kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey huye suna hai ke '' jo bhi banda Allah key wastey koi sajda kerega Allah uski wajeh sey uska eik darja buland kar dega aur uska eik gunah mita dega ''."
389,"phir meri mulaqat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey hui to mainey un sey bhi usi chiz ka sawal kya jo mainey Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey kya tha to unhoney bhi kaha ke tum sajdey ko lazim pakdo kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai ke '' jo banda Allah key wastey koi sajda kerega to Allah uski wajeh sey uska eik darja buland farmaeyga aur eik gunah mita dega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- rukoo aur sajdey kasrat sey karney key silsiley ki Soban aur Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , abu-Umama aur Abu-Fatima (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai baaz logon ka kehna hai ke namaz mein der tak qiyam karna kasrat sey rukoo aur sajda karney sey afzal hai. aur baaz ka kehna hai ke kasrat sey rukoo aur sajdey karna der tak qiyam karney sey afzal hai. Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is silsiley mein dono tarah ki hadisein marvi hain, lekin us mein) kon raajeh hai is silsiley mein) unhoney koi faisla kin baat nahin kahi hai. Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke din mein kasrat sey rukoo aur sajdey karna afzal hai aur raat mein der tak qiyam karna , illa ye ke koi shakhs aisa ho jis ka raat key hissey mein Quran padhney ka koi hissey mutayyan ho to uskey haq mein raat mein bhi rukoo aur sajdey kasrat sey karna behtar hai. kyonkey wo Quran ka itna hissey to padheyga hi jisey usney khas kar rakha hai aur kasrat sey rukoo aur sajdey ka nafa usey alag sey hasil hoga, 4- Is-haq bin Raahviya ney ye baat isliye kahi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qiyamulleil ( tahajjud (ka haal bayan kya gaya hai ke aap is mein der tak qiyam kya kartey they, rahi din ki namaz to uskey silsiley mein ye bayan nahin kya gaya hai ke aap un mein raat ki namazon ki tarah der tak qiyam kartey they."
390,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney dono kalon ko yani sanp aur bichho ko namaz mein maarney ka hukm diya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur abu-Raafey (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai, aur yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain, 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney namaz mein sanp aur bichho key maarney ko makrooh kaha hai, Ibrahim Nakhai kehtey hain ke namaz khud eik shaghl hai) aur ye chiz is mein mukhil hogi ( pehla qol ( hi ( raajeh hai."
